%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gabon%20coup%20leader%20Brice%20Nguema%20vows%20free%20elections%20-%20but%20no%20date%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693832703000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F12B54%2Fproduction%2F_130982667_gabonafp.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66705693%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22General%20Brice%20Nguema%2C%20who%20toppled%20long-time%20leader%20Ali%20Bongo%2C%20has%20officially%20become%20Gabon's%20interim%20leader.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A472%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66705693%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66705693.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-66705693.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Regulating%20OTTs%20in%20India%3A%20The%20Government%20Needs%20to%20Shift%20Its%20Focus%20From%20Content%20to%20Economics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F20124618%2Fnetflix.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20%E2%80%9Cover-the-top%E2%80%9D%20or%20OTT%20market%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Findian-ott-market-set-to-reach-30000-crore-by-2030%2Farticle66760012.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egrowing%20at%20a%2020%25%20rate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20a%20year-on-year%20(Y-o-Y)%20basis%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20touch%20Rs%2030%2C000%20crore%20by%202030.%20This%20has%20not%20only%20disrupted%20the%20mainstream%20cinema%20industry%20but%20has%20also%20democratised%20opportunities%20in%20the%20sector.%20This%20growth%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20easy%20accessibility%20of%20such%20content%20on%20our%20smartphones%20and%20the%20boost%20these%20platforms%20received%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20The%20nation-wide%20lockdown%20imposed%20during%20pandemic%20nudged%20people%20to%20seek%20entertainment%20within%20the%20confines%20of%20their%20house%2C%20making%20OTTs%20a%20convenient%20and%20affordable%20source%20of%20entertainment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMarket%20dynamics%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20OTT%20space%2C%20which%20only%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20platforms%20initially%2C%20has%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20players%20due%20to%20increased%20viewership.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20there%20are%20eight%20players%20above%20a%20viewership%20cap%20of%2030%20million%20visitors%20in%20the%20OTT%20market.%20This%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20players%2C%20as%20well%20as%20users%2C%20has%20further%20led%20companies%20to%20adopt%20innovative%20strategies%20to%20generate%20revenue%20which%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20case%20earlier.%20Such%20innovative%20strategies%20by%20OTT%20platforms%20have%20recently%20become%20a%20subject%20matter%20of%20scrutiny%20where%20the%20platforms%20are%20adopting%20various%20methods%20to%20maintain%20a%20competitive%20edge%20in%20the%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPricing%20Mechanism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20platforms%20have%20had%20to%20adjust%20their%20subscription%20fee%20to%20their%20revenue%20costs%20which%20has%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20their%20pricing%20over%20the%20last%20year.%20For%20instance%2C%20Hotstar%20recently%20increased%20its%20monthly%20subscription%20fee%20from%20Rs%20199%20to%20Rs%20299%2C%20while%20SonyLIV%20has%20increased%20it%20from%20Rs%2099%20to%20Rs%20299.%20Netflix%20being%20an%20established%20player%20in%20the%20market%20has%20been%20able%20to%20maintain%20its%20monthly%20subscription%20rate%20costing%20Rs%20499.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20median%20annual%20subscription%20fee%20for%20the%20top%20seven%20OTT%20players%20in%20the%20market%20comes%20out%20as%20Rs%20999.%20This%20amount%20is%20quite%20high%20given%20that%20the%20market%20is%20in%20its%20nascent%20stage%2C%20with%20no%20established%20loyalties%20among%20its%20subscriber%20base%20and%20a%20high%20subscriber%20attrition%20rate.%20So%20the%20players%20are%20effectively%20fighting%20for%20a%20share%20in%20an%20extremely%20volatile%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20%E2%80%98free-ride%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmidst%20this%20fight%20for%20market%20expansion%20and%20revenue%20maximisation%2C%20Jiocinema%20introduced%20yet%20another%20factor%20in%20the%20market%20which%20was%20previously%20absent.%20The%20company%20chose%20to%20stream%20IPL%20matches%20on%20its%20website%20for%20free%2C%20even%20though%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrandequity.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fmedia%2Fdisney-bets-on-free-mobile-cricket-streaming-in-india-in-battle-with-jiocinema%2F100891136%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espent%20%242.9%20bn%20on%20buying%20IPL%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%20telecasting%20rights%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20.%20The%20gains%20were%20apparent%20%E2%80%93%20even%20though%20the%20company%20lost%20on%20subscription%20revenues%2C%20it%20got%20access%20to%20millions%20of%20users%E2%80%99%20attention%20which%20was%20ultimately%20monetised%20through%20the%20sale%20of%20advertisements.%20The%20free-ride%20given%20by%20JioCinema%20has%20already%20started%20hurting%20the%20competitors%20in%20the%20market%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F05%2F10%2Fdisney-hotstar-loses-8-4-million-subscribers-as-ambani-jiocinema-takes-off%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHotstar%252C%2520which%2520counts%2520India%2520as%2CDisney%2520extend%2520beyond%2520subscriber%2520attrition.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHotstar%20facing%20a%20loss%20of%208.4%20million%20subscribers%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Esince%20October%2C%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20forcing%20it%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2023%2F06%2F09%2Fdisney-hotstar-free-mobile-cricket-streaming-jiocinema%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erecalibrate%20its%20strategy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20worthwhile%20to%20mention%20that%20YouTube%20has%20been%20offering%20free%20content%20since%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20and%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20Jiocinema%20may%20only%20be%20a%20follower.%20The%20platform%20is%20known%20to%20generate%20revenues%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20advertisements.%20It%20was%20recently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fyoutube-s-short-and-smart-future-here-re-challenges-opportunities-123061800974_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20company%20is%20planning%20to%20propel%20its%20growth%20on%20free%20content%20through%20short%20videos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20it%20may%20be%20attractive%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20no%20upfront%20costs%20for%20the%20consumers%20to%20bear%20at%20the%20surface%20level%2C%20a%20closer%20look%20would%20suggest%20otherwise%2C%20which%20is%20best%20explained%20with%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98if%20you%20are%20not%20paying%20for%20the%20product%2C%20then%20you%20are%20the%20product%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYouTube%E2%80%99s%20parent%20group%2C%20i.e.%20Google%20Inc.%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20providing%20unauthorised%20access%20of%20user%20information%20to%20advertisers%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20multiple%20scrutinies.%20The%20company%20has%20been%20found%20violating%20competition%20laws%20across%20the%20world%2C%20and%20has%20lately%20entered%20a%20grey%20area%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20data%20protection%20as%20well.%20Australian%20Competition%20and%20Consumer%20Commission%20(ACCC)%20further%20suggested%20that%20the%20lawmaker%20may%20need%20to%20come%20up%20with%20new%20legislation%20to%20address%20the%20harms%20caused%20by%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20in%20the%20Ad-Tech%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMatch%20streaming%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Relevant%20Market%20%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFree%20live%20streaming%20of%20sports%20services%20may%20further%20suggest%20it%20as%20a%20separate%20relevant%20market%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20promoting%20competition.%20The%20Indian%20competition%20commission%2C%20though%20in%20a%20different%20set%20of%20facts%20and%20circumstances%2C%20held%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cci.gov.in%2Fantitrust%2Forders%2Fdetails%2F760%2F0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecricket%20matches%20cannot%20be%20substituted%20with%20other%20entertainment%20channels%20and%20movies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Therefore%2C%20viewers%20of%20live%20sports%20may%20be%20considered%20as%20a%20distinct%20category.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESustained%20growth%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20a%20market%20economics%20point%20of%20view%2C%20it%20remains%20imperative%20that%20the%20incumbents%20aren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20offer%20free%20services%20for%20long.%20This%20may%20be%20truer%20for%20entrenched%20players%20in%20the%20economy.%20Such%20a%20strategy%20has%20constantly%20invited%20scrutiny%20from%20competition%20bodies%20across%20the%20globe.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20India%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Reliance%20Jio%20with%20free-services%20was%20marred%20with%20multiple%20complaints.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20sector-based%20regulation%2C%20it%20was%20alleged%20that%20such%20free%20services%20not%20only%20fall%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20predatory%20pricing%2C%20but%20also%20allow%20Reliance%20Industries%20as%20a%20group%20to%20fuel%20its%20entry%20in%20the%20telecom%20market%20through%20dominance%20in%20other%20relevant%20markets%20%E2%80%93%20both%20the%20practices%20prohibited%20under%20express%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Competition%20Act.%20Even%20though%20the%20telecom%20industry%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time%20was%20flourishing%20with%20multiple%20players%20in%20the%20market%2C%20Reliance%20Industries%E2%80%99%20deep%20pockets%20allowed%20it%20to%20fund%20its%20new%20service%20well%20beyond%20the%20prescribed%20time%20limit%2C%20thereby%20resulting%20in%20multiple%20exits%20of%20competing%20players%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20an%20apparent%20implication%20on%20the%20consumer-welfare%20standard.%20Promotion%20of%20such%20a%20standard%20has%20been%20a%20long-sought%20goal%20of%20various%20economic%20legislations%20and%20therefore%2C%20it%20becomes%20important%20for%20the%20government%20to%20conduct%20detailed%20stakeholder%20consultation%20so%20that%20economically%20efficient%20outcomes%20are%20achieved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20focus%20has%20been%20on%20regulating%20the%20content%20on%20such%20platforms%2C%20it%20may%20be%20high%20time%20for%20it%20to%20assess%20the%20market%20potential%20and%20subsequent%20competition%20concerns%20which%20may%20be%20arising%20out%20of%20it.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20nodal%20Indian%20competition%20regulator%20has%20been%20taking%20such%20industry-specific%20studies%20from%20time%20to%20time%20as%20part%20of%20its%20mandate.%20While%20the%20dynamic%20nature%20of%20the%20entertainment%20industry%20may%20require%20the%20government%20to%20periodically%20review%20its%20position%20while%20regulating%2C%20the%20provision%20of%20%E2%80%98free%E2%80%99%20services%2C%20irrespective%20of%20live%20streaming%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20separate%20RM%2C%20warrants%20a%20second%20look%20especially%20when%20offered%20by%20industry%20giants.%20A%20thorough%20review%20of%20the%20sector%20is%20required%C2%A0given%20that%20until%20now%20the%20model%20has%20been%20that%20of%20charging%20a%20subscription%20fee%20for%20the%20services%20provided.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20OTT%20market%20is%20in%20a%20growing%20phase.%20While%20there%20may%20be%20immense%20potential%20in%20the%20market%20to%20be%20explored%2C%20price%20warfare%2C%20a%20sign%20of%20brewing%20maturity%2C%20has%20already%20begun.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20digital%20markets%2C%20regulations%20should%20follow%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20industry%20rather%20than%20trailing%20behind.%20In%20the%20world%20of%20ex-ante%20regulations%2C%20Indian%20regulators%20should%20invest%20time%20and%20resources%20in%20conducting%20research%20and%20study%20on%20digital%20markets%20and%20engaging%20with%20all%20the%20relevant%20stakeholders%20before%20arriving%20at%20any%20policy%20decision..%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20larger%20goal%20should%20be%20to%20make%20economically%20efficient%20law%20and%20policies%20in%20the%20betterment%20of%20consumers%20without%20warping%20the%20market%20principles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESumit%20Jain%20is%20a%20director%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Competition%20Law%20and%20Economics%20and%20Abhishek%20Raj%20is%20a%20consultant%20at%20the%20CCLE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693831824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2F20124618%2Fnetflix.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fregulating-otts-in-india-the-government-needs-to-shift-its-focus-from-content-to-economics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20it%20comes%20to%20digital%20markets%2C%20regulations%20should%20follow%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20industry%20rather%20than%20trailing%20behind.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fregulating-otts-in-india-the-government-needs-to-shift-its-focus-from-content-to-economics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%