killed-encounter-underway-in-jammu-and-kashmirs-reasi-4358842%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorist-killed-encounter-underway-in-jammu-and-kashmirs-reasi-4358842%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israelis%20held%20in%20Cyprus%20over%20alleged%20rape%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693831040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FB8E0%2Fproduction%2F_130982374_aiyanapagettyimages-1234572141.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66707626%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20foreign%20ministry%20says%20six%20citizens%20were%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20raping%20a%20British%20tourist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66707626%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66707626.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-66707626.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fresh%20Adani%20Revelations%20that%20Hint%20at%20Regulator%20SEBI%20Inaction%20Could%20Hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20FATF%20Credibility%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F21181904%2Fadani-brothers.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20(FATF)%20review%20of%20India%20currently%20underway%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20signals%20emanating%20from%20the%20kid%20glove%20treatment%20meted%20out%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20by%20various%20investigative%20agencies%20and%20market%20watchdog%2C%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20inability%20or%20unwillingness%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20serious%20charges%20of%20round%20tripping%20or%20the%20flow%20of%20money%20from%20and%20to%20tax%20havens%20allegedly%20around%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20and%20fastest%20growing%20conglomerate%20could%20have%20a%20series%20of%20unintended%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20consequence%20could%20be%20a%20shadow%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20integrity%20as%20a%20responsible%20system%20having%20institutional%20heft%20to%20know%20about%2C%20and%20prevent%2C%20illegal%20flows%20of%20money%20across%20its%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FATF%20is%20the%20global%20money%20laundering%20and%20terrorist%20financing%20watchdog.%20According%20to%20its%20own%20definition%2C%20it%20%E2%80%9Csets%20international%20standards%20that%20aim%20to%20prevent%20these%20illegal%20activities%20and%20the%20harm%20they%20cause%20to%20society%E2%80%9D.%20North%20Korea%2C%20Iran%20and%20Myanmar%20are%20currently%20on%20the%20FATF%20black%20list.%20It%20was%20only%20in%20October%202022%20that%20Pakistan%20after%20four%20years%20of%20finding%20itself%20on%20the%20grey%20list%20and%20facing%20serious%20financial%20strictures%2C%20could%20manage%20to%20make%20its%20way%20off%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20SEBI%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20the%20alleged%20stock%20price%20manipulation%20in%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20at%20least%20one%20investigation%20was%20contingent%20on%20receiving%20crucial%20data%20from%20overseas%2C%20pending%20which%20it%20cannot%20go%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20submission%20will%20hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20case%20as%20this%20is%20a%20direct%20violation%20of%20Outcome%20number%20two%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fatf-gafi.org%2Fen%2Fpublications%2FMutualevaluations%2FFatf-methodology.html%5C%22%3EFATF%20guidelines.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20telling%20the%20court%20that%20it%20is%20awaiting%20information%20from%20overseas%2C%20SEBI%20is%20essentially%20admitting%20that%20a%20robust%20international%20cooperation%20is%20lacking%2C%20which%20is%20what%20Outcome%202%20is%20all%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22To%20Legalise%20Power%20Project%20Given%20to%20Adani%20Without%20Tender%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Wants%20it%20Turned%20Into%20Govt-to-Govt%20Deal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fto-legalise-power-project-given-to-adani-without-tender-sri-lanka-wants-it-turned-into-govt-to-govt-deal%5C%22%3ETo%20Legalise%20Power%20Project%20Given%20to%20Adani%20Without%20Tender%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Wants%20it%20Turned%20Into%20Govt-to-Govt%20Deal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FATF%20review%20by%20the%20UN%20body%20follows%2040%20recommendations%20and%2011%20outcomes%20while%20doing%20a%20country%20review.%20The%20recommendations%20are%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20robust%20laws%2C%20rules%20and%20regulations%20being%20in%20place%20and%20the%20outcome%20is%20about%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20implementing%20these%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20who%20are%20familiar%20with%20the%20workings%20of%20the%20FATF%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20incumbent%20on%20the%20country%20to%20get%20the%20information%20it%20is%20asking%20for%20because%20if%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20get%20the%20information%2C%20it%20means%20our%20request%20was%20not%20as%20per%20the%20law%20or%20was%20lacking%20in%20some%20way.%20The%20FATF%20looks%20at%20the%20broader%20prospective%20of%20international%20cooperation%20as%20well%20as%20robust%20domestic%20coordination.%20Our%20ratings%20are%20likely%20to%20fall%20on%20the%20domestic%20front%20as%20well.%20Weak%20coordination%20between%20various%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20no%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20Adani%20group%20by%20any%20federal%20or%20state%20agency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%20had%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20August%2025%20that%20data%20from%20five%20offshore%20tax%20havens%20was%20awaited%20which%20will%20identify%20the%20end%20beneficiaries%20behind%20foreign%20investors%20who%20are%20engaged%20with%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20days%20later%2C%20a%20report%20by%20a%20consortium%20of%20investigative%20reporters%2C%20from%20the%20OCCRP%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20asserted%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20documents%20accessed%20by%20them%20that%20the%20Adani%20group%20has%20invested%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20its%20own%20companies%20through%20a%20complex%20web%20of%20offshore%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20also%20said%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20had%20alerted%20SEBI%20about%20suspicious%20transactions%20of%20these%20off%20shore%20entities%20as%20early%20as%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20SEBI%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20it%20had%20information%20coming%20in%20only%20as%20late%20as%202020%2C%20after%20which%20it%20started%20its%20enquiries.%20SEBI%20has%20been%20silent%20on%20if%20it%20has%20investigated%20the%20leads%20given%20to%20it%20by%20the%20DRI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESEBI%E2%80%99s%20actions%20or%20the%20lack%20of%20them%20impact%20Outcome%203%20and%204%20of%20FATF%20because%20of%20the%20failure%20of%20SEBI%20and%20RBI%20to%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20tabs%20on%20where%20funds%20for%20the%20Adani%20group%20are%20coming%20from.%20The%20RBI%20is%20supposed%20to%20maintain%20the%20balance%20of%20payments%20position.%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20role%20as%20the%20gatekeeper%20of%20%C2%A0the%20flow%20of%20money%20incoming%20and%20outgoing%20from%20India%20is%20also%20assessed%20during%20an%20FATF%20review.%20It%20too%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20raise%20questions%20about%20alleged%20illicit%20flow%20of%20money.%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20effectiveness%20is%20one%20of%20the%2011%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22How%20the%20Black%20Money%20Was%20Brought%20Back%20to%20India%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fhow-the-black-money-was-brought-back-to-india%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Black%20Money%20Was%20Brought%20Back%20to%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20group%20has%20dubbed%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20as%20baseless%20and%20and%20the%20OCCRP%20findings%20as%20%E2%80%9Crecycled%20allegations%E2%80%9D.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Fadani%2F%5C%22%3EJanuary%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20dubbed%20the%20Adani%20group%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Clargest%20con%20in%20corporate%20history%E2%80%9D%20shaved%20off%20a%20%24100%20billion%20worth%20of%20the%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20various%20verticals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmediate%20outcome%207%20of%20FATF%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20be%20impacted%20going%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fhindenburg-spotlights-an-offshore-adani-related-entity-that-ed-had-linked-to-agustawestland-scam%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3Ethis%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20shows%20a%20failure%20of%20a%20domestic%20federal%20agency%2C%20or%20its%20inability%20to%20take%20a%20prosecution%20to%20a%20logical%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20in%20February%20this%20year%20reported%20that%20an%20Adani%20company%2C%20Gudami%20International%20Pte%20Ltd%2C%20had%20been%20one%20of%20the%20alleged%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Agusta%20Westland%20VVIP%20chopper%20deal%20slush%20funds.%20The%20company%20figured%20in%20two%20chargesheets%20filed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%202014%20and%202015%20where%20details%20of%20how%20the%20bribes%20were%20paid%20was%20shared.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20ED%20sent%20a%20Letter%20Rogatory%20to%20Singapore%20where%20Gudami%20International%20was%20registered.%20In%20the%20third%20chargesheet%2C%20while%20several%20other%20companies%20and%20the%20Singapore%20information%20were%20mentioned%2C%20Gudami%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COutcome%208%20too%20is%20impacted%20because%20since%20there%20is%20no%20conviction%20in%20this%20case%2C%20there%20is%20no%20confiscation%20of%20property%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Gudami%20International%20Pte%20Ltd%2C%E2%80%9D%20officials%20familiar%20with%20the%20case%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20anti%20money%20laundering%20agency%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20or%20ED%E2%80%99s%20not%20too%20stellar%20record%20also%20directly%20impacts%20Outcome%207%20and%208%20of%20the%20FATF.%20While%20Outcome%207%20deals%20with%20prosecution%20and%20convictions%2C%20Outcome%208%20deals%20with%20confiscation%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20its%20website%2C%20the%20agency%20has%20a%20conviction%20rate%20of%2096%25%2C%20politicians%20comprise%20only%203%25%20of%20all%20cases%20and%20search%20warrants%20were%20issued%20in%208.99%25%20of%20the%20cases.%20But%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98conviction%20rate%E2%80%99%20is%20based%20on%2024%20out%20of%2025%20cases%20in%20which%20a%20PMLA%20trial%20was%20completed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIANS%20quoting%20finance%20ministry%20sources%20reported%20that%20between%202018-19%20and%202021-22%2C%20cases%20registered%20by%20ED%20rose%20by%20505%25%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2F505-rise-in-cases-registered-by-ed-since-2018-1205886.html%5C%22%3Efrom%20195%20cases%20in%202018-19%2C%20to%201%2C180%20in%202021-22%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20number%20of%20searches%20the%20ED%20conducted%20rose%20by%20a%20huge%202%2C555%25%20between%202004-14%20and%202014-22.%20As%20per%20finance%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20own%20data%2C%20112%20searches%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20ED%20between%202004-14%20resulting%20in%20attachment%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20worth%20Rs%205%2C346%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20gave%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0a%20three-page%20response%20to%20its%20queries%2C%20but%20some%20questions%20regarding%20the%20role%20of%20the%20agency%20remain%20unanswered%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20cases%20has%20the%20investigation%20been%20completed%20so%20trial%20can%20commence%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20cases%20have%20been%20registered%20and%20closed%20by%20way%20of%20discharge%20or%20quashing%20or%20acquittal%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20accused%20have%20been%20discharged%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20filed%20in%20court%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20properties%20attached%2C%20how%20many%20have%20been%20confiscated%20by%20the%20ED%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20ED%20had%20then%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tenor%20and%20content%20of%20your%20letter%20shows%20that%20it%20is%20based%20not%20only%20on%20incorrect%20and%20misleading%20facts%20but%20also%20shows%20that%20you%20have%20not%20conducted%20proper%20research%20including%20checking%20the%20website%20of%20the%20ED.%20Otherwise%2C%20you%20have%20not%20put%20certain%20questions%20relating%20to%20statistics%20and%20asked%20for%20answers%20from%20us.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20letter%20is%20to%20do%20a%20roving%20inquiry%20for%20an%20oblique%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ED%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsk-mishra-enforcement-directorate-fatf-evaluation%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20time%20that%20FATF%20was%20in%20the%20news%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20when%20the%20Modi%20government%20was%20arguing%20for%20the%20retention%20of%20ED%20Director%2C%20Sanjay%20Mishra%2C%20in%20the%20face%20of%20stiff%20resistance%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20Modi%20government%20had%20repeatedly%20invoked%20the%20FATF%20review%20as%20crucial%20and%20underlined%20the%20role%20Mishra%20was%20playing%20in%20seeing%20India%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693830657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F21181904%2Fadani-brothers.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffresh-adani-revelations-that-hint-at-regulator-sebi-inaction-could-hurt-indias-fatf-credibility%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20review%20by%20the%20global%20money%20laundering%20and%20terrorist%20financing%20watchdog%20is%20underway%20and%20an%20impression%20that%20regulators%20are%20ignorant%20or%20unwilling%20to%20act%20on%20charges%20of%20illegal%20money%20flows%20could%20be%20detrimental%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20credibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffresh-adani-revelations-that-hint-at-regulator-sebi-inaction-could-hurt-indias-fatf-credibility%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Asia%20Cup%20Live%3A%20Full%20Ground%20Under%20Covers%2C%20India%20And%20Nepal%20Wait%20Anxiously%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20vs%20Nepal%2C%20Asia%20Cup%202023%2C%20Live%20Updates%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERain%20has%20interrupted%20the%20proceedings%20of%20the%20match%20and%20the%20covers%20have%20been%20brought%20back%20on%20the%20field.%20Before%20the%20halt%2C%20Nepal's%20score%20read%20at%20178%2F6%20in%2037.5%20overs%20with%20Sompal%20Kami%20and%20Dipendra%20Singh%20standing%20unbeaten%20at%20the%20crease.%3Cb%3E%20%3C%2Fb%3EIndia%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bowl%20against%20Nepal%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20match%20on%20Monday.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIndia%20will%20be%20missing%20out%20on%20the%20services%20of%20their%20star%20pacer%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami%20has%20been%20named%20as%20his%20replacement.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22h