0to%20see%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20law%20professors%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20studied%20this%20issue%3B%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4480628%5C%22%3Eour%20research%20shows%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20is%20no%20recognised%20property%20right%20under%20US%20law%20%E2%80%93%20or%20the%20laws%20of%20any%20other%20country%20of%20which%20we%20are%20aware%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20facts%20and%20events%20that%20occur%20during%20someone%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20are%20Oher%2C%20Tyson%20and%20others%20complaining%3F%20And%20why%20do%20publishers%20and%20studios%20routinely%20pay%20large%20sums%20to%20acquire%20rights%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20monopoly%20on%20the%20truth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20states%2C%20the%20commercial%20use%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20image%20and%20likeness%20is%20protected%20by%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frightofpublicityroadmap.com%2F%5C%22%3Eright%20of%20publicity%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20But%20that%20right%20generally%20applies%20to%20merchandise%2C%20apparel%20and%20product%20endorsements%2C%20not%20facts%20and%20actual%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20sell%20a%20T-shirt%20with%20Mike%20Tyson%E2%80%99s%20face%20on%20it%20without%20his%20permission%2C%20but%20writing%20a%20book%20about%20his%20rise%20to%20fame%20is%20fair%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20freedom%20to%20describe%20historical%20events%20is%20rooted%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconstitution.congress.gov%2Fbrowse%2Fessay%2Famdt1-7-1%2FALDE_00013537%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20free%20speech%20clause%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20the%20First%20Amendment%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20fundamental%20principle%20that%20no%20one%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20news%20agency%2C%20political%20party%20or%20celebrity%20%E2%80%93%20holds%20a%20monopoly%20on%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2016%2F03%2F19%2Fbusiness%2Fmedia%2Fgawker-hulk-hogan-verdict.html%5C%22%3EThe%20law%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20sanction%20the%20invasion%20of%20privacy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20an%20investigative%20journalist%20who%20uncovers%20some%20unsavoury%20detail%20of%20your%20past%20can%E2%80%99t%20publish%20it%20unless%20there%20is%20a%20legitimate%20public%20interest%20in%20doing%20so.%20Nor%20does%20it%20condone%20the%20dissemination%20of%20false%20information%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2023%2F04%2F18%2Fbusiness%2Ffox-news-dominion-trial-settlement%5C%22%3Ewhich%20can%20lead%20to%20defamation%20lawsuits%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20First%20Amendment%2C%20however%2C%20does%20allow%20authors%20and%20film%20producers%20to%20truthfully%20depict%20factual%20events%20that%20they%20have%20legitimately%20learned%20about.%20They%20are%20not%20required%20to%20receive%20authorisation%20from%20or%20pay%20the%20people%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20origin%20of%20life%20story%20%E2%80%98rights%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilm%20producers%2C%20however%2C%20are%20accustomed%20to%20paying%20for%20the%20right%20to%20repackage%20or%20use%20existing%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECopyright%20licenses%20are%20required%20to%20commission%20a%20script%20based%20on%20a%20book%2C%20to%20depict%20a%20comic%20book%20character%20in%20a%20film%20and%20to%20include%20a%20hit%20song%20on%20a%20movie%20soundtrack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20showing%20an%20architecturally%20distinctive%20building%20often%20requires%20the%20consent%20of%20a%20copyright%20owner%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20video%20game%20%E2%80%9CSpider-Man%3A%20Miles%20Morales%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ign.com%2Farticles%2Fspider-man-miles-morales-doesnt-have-the-chrysler-building-due-to-copyright-issues%5C%22%3Ehad%20to%20remove%20the%20Chrysler%20Building%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20576px)%2085vw%2C%20576px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04152752%2FChrysler-building.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04152752%2FChrysler-building.jpg%20576w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04152752%2FChrysler-building-288x300.jpg%20288w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671383%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EStudios%20hoping%20to%20include%20a%20shot%20of%20the%20Chrysler%20Building%20in%20their%20films%20might%20have%20to%20pony%20up.%20Photo%3A%20Carlos%20Delgado%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%20Unported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20these%20other%20rights%20and%20permissions%2C%20Hollywood%20studios%20have%20paid%20individuals%20for%20their%20life%20stories%20for%20at%20least%20a%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20unlike%20copyright%20clearances%2C%20life%20story%20deals%20do%20not%20involve%20the%20acquisition%20of%20known%20intellectual%20property%20rights.%20Life%20story%20%E2%80%9Crights%E2%80%9D%20are%20not%20rights%20at%20all.%20Instead%2C%20they%20bundle%20together%20a%20set%20of%20contractual%20commitments%3A%20the%20subject%E2%80%99s%20agreement%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20studio%2C%20not%20to%20work%20on%20a%20similar%20project%2C%20and%20to%20release%20the%20studio%20from%20claims%20of%20defamation%20and%20invasion%20of%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20packaging%20these%20commitments%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20%E2%80%9Clife%20story%20rights%E2%80%9D%2C%20studios%20can%20signal%20to%20the%20market%20that%20they%20have%20acquired%20a%20particularly%20juicy%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Netflix%E2%80%99s%20quick%20deal%20with%20convicted%20fraudster%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fhow-scammers-like-anna-delvey-and-the-tinder-swindler-exploit-a-core-feature-of-human-nature-177289%5C%22%3EAnna%20Sorokin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20subject%20of%20the%20popular%20streaming%20series%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt8740976%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EInventing%20Anna%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-56113478%5C%22%3Edeterred%20competing%20adaptations%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20Sorokin%E2%80%99s%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20the%20acquisition%20of%20life%20story%20rights%20has%20become%20so%20common%20that%20it%20is%20viewed%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20as%20a%20de%20facto%20requirement%20for%20film%20financing%20and%20insurance%20coverage%20and%20thus%20part%20of%20the%20standard%20clearance%20procedure%20for%20many%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExceptions%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20the%20rule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20always%20with%20the%20law%2C%20though%2C%20there%20are%20exceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20producers%20of%20the%202010%20film%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Social%20Network%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fperma.cc%2FSN4H-UXAP%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20obtain%20the%20permission%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Facebook%20founder%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20before%20dramatising%20the%20origin%20story%20of%20his%20company.%20In%20moving%20forward%20with%20the%20project%2C%20they%20risked%20a%20defamation%20or%20publicity%20suit%20by%20Zuckerberg%20and%20others%20depicted%20in%20the%20film.%20But%20their%20gamble%20paid%20off%3A%20Zuckerberg%2C%20while%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fperma.cc%2FSN4H-UXAP%5C%22%3Ecritical%20of%20his%20depiction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20sue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20other%20subjects%20who%20have%20been%20depicted%20in%20dramatic%20features%20without%20their%20authorisation%20have%20sued%20to%20recover%20a%20share%20of%20the%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESilver%20screen%20legend%20Olivia%20de%20Havilland%2C%20for%20example%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasetext.com%2Fcase%2Fde-havilland-v-fx-networks-llc-1%5C%22%3Esued%20FX%20Studios%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20briefly%20depicting%20her%20in%20a%20miniseries%20about%20Hollywood%20rivals%20Bette%20Davis%20and%20Joan%20Crawford.%20She%20won%20at%20trial%2C%20though%20an%20appeals%20court%20reversed%20her%20victory%2C%20citing%20the%20producers%E2%80%99%20First%20Amendment%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawsuits%20can%20even%20be%20brought%20when%20the%20characters%E2%80%99%20names%20and%20story%20details%20have%20been%20changed.%20US%20Army%20Sgt.%20Jeffrey%20Sarver%2C%20the%20bomb-defusing%20expert%20who%20inspired%20the%20Oscar-winning%20film%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Ftitle%2Ftt0887912%2F%3Fref_%3Dnv_sr_srsg_0_tt_8_nm_0_q_the%252520hurt%252520locker%5C%22%3EThe%20Hurt%20Locker%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcasetext.com%2Fcase%2Fsarver-v-chartier%5C%22%3Esued%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20producers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20violating%20his%20right%20of%20publicity.%20He%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawsuits%20like%20these%20are%20not%20the%20norm.%20But%20many%20producers%20hope%20to%20get%20ahead%20of%20a%20flimsy%20lawsuit%20and%20bad%20publicity%20by%20acquiring%20nonexistent%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistory%20is%20in%20the%20public%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Edomain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20and%20much%20that%20is%20right%20%E2%80%93%20with%20paying%20individuals%20to%20cooperate%20with%20the%20production%20of%20features%20about%20themselves.%20Doing%20so%20can%20convey%20respect%20toward%20the%20subject%20and%20make%20the%20production%20go%20more%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fact%20that%20life%20story%20acquisitions%20have%20entered%20the%20popular%20consciousness%20has%20spurred%20the%20widespread%20belief%20that%20any%20portrayal%20of%20a%20factual%20series%20of%20events%20entitles%20those%20depicted%20to%20a%20lucrative%20payday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20expectation%20increases%20production%20costs%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20litigation%2C%20thereby%20deterring%20otherwise%20worthwhile%20projects%20and%20depriving%20the%20public%20of%20meaningful%20content%20that%20is%20based%20on%20true%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20be%20done%20about%20this%20situation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20idea%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4480628%5C%22%3Ethat%20we%E2%80%99ve%20written%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0would%20prevent%20right%20of%20publicity%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20the%20basis%20for%20many%20life%20story%20lawsuits%20%E2%80%93%20from%20being%20used%20against%20works%20that%20convey%20ideas%20and%20tell%20a%20story%2C%20such%20as%20books%2C%20films%20and%20TV%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20that%20can%20be%20done%2C%20though%2C%20is%20educating%20people%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20right%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20every%20description%20of%20the%20events%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollective%20history%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%20belongs%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJorge%20L.%20Contreras%2C%20James%20T.%20Jensen%20Endowed%20Professor%20for%20Transactional%20Law%20and%20Director%2C%20Program%20on%20Intellectual%20Property%20and%20Technology%20Law%2C%20University%20of%20Utah%3B%20and%20Dave%20Fagundes%2C%20Baker%20Botts%20LLP%20Professor%20of%20Law%20and%20Research%20Dean%2C%20University%20of%20Houston%20Law%20Center.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fmichael-oher-mike-tyson-and-the-question-of-whether-you-own-your-life-story-212242%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693824313000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04154720%2FMike-Tyson.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fcan-you-own-your-life-story%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Life%20story%20acquisitions%E2%80%99%20have%20led%20to%20the%20belief%20that%20any%20portrayal%20of%20a%20factual%20series%20of%20events%20entitles%20those%20depicted%20to%20a%20lucrative%20payday.%20But%20is%20this%20true%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fcan-you-own-your-life-story%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi's%20Palam%20Airbase%20To%20Welcome%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%2070%20VVIP%20Jets%20For%20G20%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20has%20made%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20arrangements%26quot%3B%20to%20land%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20nearly%2070%20VVIP%20aircraft%20at%20the%20Palam%20Technical%20Airport%20-%20an%20airbase%20-%20when%20world%20leaders%20begin%20arriving%20in%20India%20for%20the%20mega%20G20%20Summit%20later%20this%20week.%20Four%20other%20airports%20-%20identified%20as%20%26quot%3Breserved%20airports%26quot%3B%20-%20have%20been%20marked%20for%20any%20contingencies%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarting%20September%207%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20fighter%20planes%20will%20be%20on%20standby%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20any%20suspicious%20activity%20in%20the%20Delhi%20sky%2C%20including%20of%20UAVs%20or%20drones%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20functionary%20in%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContingency%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Indore%2C%20and%20Amritsar%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20PK%20Mishra%2C%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20Delhi's%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Vinai%20Kumar%20Saxena%20oversaw%20the%20arrangements%20at%20Palam%20Technical%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20reserved%20airports%20were%20identified%20at%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20with%20officials%20from%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20Security%20(BCAS)%2C%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi%20International%20Airport%20Limited%20(DIAL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Air%20Traffic%20Control%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20be%20on%20high%20alert%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%20and%20closely%20monitor%20all%20flights%20entering%20Delhi.%20In%20case%20of%20any%20emergency%20situation%2C%20flights%20will%20be%20diverted%20to%20any%20of%20the%20four%20other%20airports%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20contingency%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20senior%20official%20handling%20G20%20security%20arrangements%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20VIPs%20will%20land%20at%20the%20technical%20airport%20but%20aircraft%20and%20private%20jets%20carrying%20them%20will%20be%20parked%20at%20the%20Delhi%20airport.%20Special%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20to%20park%20the%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20a%20few%20other%20important%20aircraft%20at%20the%20Palam%20Air%20Force%20Station.%20The%20station%20is%20under%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20VVIP%20aircraft%20will%20be%20parked%20in%20Bay-1%20and%20Bay-3%20of%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20as%20they%20are%20very%20close%20to%20the%20ceremonial%20lounge%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20parking%20spaces%20have%20been%20identified%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20Terminal-1%2C%20and%20the%20cargo%20terminal.%20%26quot%3BAround%2018%20aircraft%20will%20be%20accommodated%20at%20the%20Palam%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20we%20have%20already%20made%20provisions%20for%20the%20required%20parking%20of%20aircraft%20at%20Delhi%20Airport.%20Our%20top%20priority%20remains%20ensuring%20a%20smooth%20and%20efficient%20travel%20experience%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Airport%20boasts%20an%20impressive%20parking%20capacity%20of%2072%20charter%20aircraft%2C%20along%20with%20a%20dedicated%20terminal.%20The%20DIAL%20officials%20maintained%20that%20the%20current%20flight%20cancellations%20were%20not%20linked%20to%20the%20availability%20of%20parking%20spaces%20for%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20received%20requests%20from%20airlines%20for%20the%20cancellation%20of%20approximately%2080%20arrivals%20and%2080%20departures%20as%20of%20now.%20However%2C%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20working%20closely%20with%20airlines%20to%20minimize%20any%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20reassure%20all%20travellers%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20is%20fully%20equipped%20with%20ample%20parking%20for%20aircraft.%20Despite%20the%20cancellations%2C%20we%20are%20pleased%20to%20report%20that%20the%20restrictions%20will%20not%20impact%20international%20flights.%20The%20cancellations%20only%20account%20for%20approximately%20six%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20normal%20domestic%20operations%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20over%20the%20span%20of%20three%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20have%20made%20extensive%20arrangements%20for%20world%20leaders%20to%20travel%20from%20the%20airport%20to%20their%20respective%20hotels%20where%20they%20would%20be%20staying%20during%20the%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693824000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4d0gqb2g_delhi-traffic-police-g20-summit-ani_625x300_02_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-palam-airbase-to-welcome-air-force-one-70-vvip-jets-for-g20-4358398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20has%20made%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20arrangements%26quot%3B%20to%20land%20nearly%2070%20VVIP%20aircraft%20at%20the%20Palam%20Technical%20Airport%20-%20an%20airbase%20-%20when%20world%20leaders%20begin%20arriving%20in%20India%20for%20the%20mega%20G20%20Summit%20later%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-palam-airbase-to-welcome-air-force-one-70-vvip-jets-for-g20-4358398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-palam-airbase-to-welcome-air-force-one-70-vvip-jets-for-g20-4358398%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-palam-airbase-to-welcome-air-force-one-70-vvip-jets-for-g20-4358398%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20Engineer%2C%2022%2C%20Plans%20To%20Retire%20At%2035%20With%20Savings%20Of%20Rs%2041%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMost%20young%20people%2C%20these%20days%2C%20aspire%20to%20save%20and%20invest%20enough%20money%20so%20they%20can%20retire%20early.%20One%20such%20person%20is%C2%A0Ethan%20Nguonly%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20software%20engineer%20at%20Google%2C%20who%20is%20aiming%20for%20an%20early%20retirement%20with%20a%20target%20of%20accumulating%20%245%20million%20(roughly%20Rs%2041%20crore)%20by%20the%20age%20of%2035%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F08%2F31%2F22-year-old-earns-194k-a-year-as-a-software-engineer-at-google.html%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20techie%2C%20%C2%A0living%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California%2C%20credited%20his%20parents%20for%C2%A0teaching%20him%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20investing%20money%20in%20stocks%20rather%20than%20just%20saving%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''%E2%80%B3%5BMy%20parents%5D%20really%20explained%20it%20to%20me%20well%2C%20They%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20leave%20your%20money%20here%20%5Bin%20a%20savings%20account%5D%2C%20over%20time%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20become%20worthless%2C'%20and%20they%20said%20that%20you%20should%20really%20learn%20to%20invest%20it%20into%20something%2C''%20Mr%20Nguonly%20told%20%3Cem%3ECNBC%20Make%20It.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20the%20main%20thing%20I%20was%20thinking%20about%20was%2C%20'All%20this%20money%20keeps%20getting%20bigger%2C%20keeps%20growing%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20doing%20any%20work%20for%20this%2C'.%C2%A0This%20really%20exposed%20me%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20my%20investments%20could%20make%20me%20money%20instead%20of%20me%20actually%20having%20to%20actively%20work%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20determination%20to%20achieve%20financial%20freedom%20led%20him%20to%C2%A0complete%20his%20computer%20science%20degree%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20in%20just%20two%20years%2C%20avoiding%20student%20debt.%20He%20also%20opted%20to%20stay%20with%20his%20family%20after%20completing%20his%20bachelor's%20degree%20to%20save%20money%20on%20rent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%C2%A0secured%20a%20job%20at%20a%20software%20company%20while%20simultaneously%20starting%20his%C2%A0master's%20degree%20in%C2%A0information%20and%20data%20science.%20He%20completed%20the%20course%20in%20August%202022.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20getting%20his%20master's%2C%20he%20also%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20Google%20as%20a%20software%20engineer.%20He%20has%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20%24194%2C000%20(roughly%20Rs%201.60%20crore)%2C%20inclusive%20of%20bonuses%20and%20stock%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%C2%A0he%20also%20has%20close%20to%20%24135%2C000%20(Rs%C2%A01.11%20crore)%20invested%20across%20his%20retirement%20and%20other%20investment%20accounts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20homes%20in%20Florida%20and%20California.%20He%20aims%20to%20invest%2035%25%20of%20his%20take-home%20pay%20each%20year%20and%20plans%20to%20expand%20his%20real%20estate%20portfolio%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Nguonly%20bought%20an%20investment%20property%20in%20Riverview%2C%20Florida%20at%20the%20start%20of%202022%20and%20about%20a%20year%20later%2C%20bought%20his%20primary%20residence%20in%20La%20Palma%2C%20California%20where%20he%20lives%20with%20his%20dog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20spend%20too%20much%20money%20on%20food%20because%20Google%20provides%20free%20breakfast%20and%20lunch.%20Further%2C%20he%20doesn't%20believe%20in%20splurging%20on%20brand-name%20clothes%20and%20prefers%20to%20wear%20simplistic%20and%20affordable%20clothes.%20While%20he%20loves%20traveling%20and%20usually%20takes%20three%20to%20four%20trips%20a%20year%2C%20he%20sticks%20to%20lower-cost%20options%20rather%20than%20luxury%20upgrades%2C%C2%A0such%20as%20sharing%20an%20Airbnb%20with%20a%20friend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reach%20his%20%245%20million%20goal%2C%20he%20plans%20to%20continue%20investing%20in%20his%20retirement%20accounts%20and%20adding%20to%20his%20real%20estate%20portfolio%20by%20buying%20a%20new%20property%20every%20couple%20of%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20a%20book%20that%20really%20inspired%20him%20on%20his%20journey%2C%20he%20said%2C%20''It%20talks%20about%20how%20you%20should%20spend%20more%20money%20on%20experiences%20and%20travel%20while%20you're%20still%20young%20and%20healthy.%20This%20is%20why%20I%20really%20set%20out%20this%20goal.%C2%A0I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%2067%20years%20old%20trying%20to%20climb%20up%20some%20mountain%2C%20I'd%20rather%20do%20it%20while%20I'm%20still%20able%20to%20fully%20enjoy%20these%20experiences.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F40cmfqso_google-generic_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20has%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20%24194%2C000%20(roughly%20Rs%201.60%20crore)%2C%20inclusive%20of%20bonuses%20and%20stock%20units.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Quran%20burnings%20in%20Europe%20spark%20debate%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823538000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103356899%2Cimgsize-1195200.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fquran-burnings-in-sweden-denmark-prompt-debate-on-fine-line-between-freedom-of-expression-and-incitement-of-hatred%2Farticleshow%2F103354535.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20immigrant%20neighbourhood%20in%20Sweden's%20third%20largest%20city%20witnessed%20violent%20clashes%20yet%20again%20after%20an%20'anti-Islam'%20protester%20set%20fire%20to%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Quran.%20Police%20in%20Malmo%20said%20they%20were%20pelted%20with%20rocks%20and%20dozens%20of%20cars%20were%20set%20on%20fire%2C%20describing%20the%20events%20that%20started%20on%20Sunday%20and%20lasted%20overnight%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20violent%20riot%26quot%3B.%20At%20least%20three%20people%20have%20been%20detained%20so%20far.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fquran-burnings-in-sweden-denmark-prompt-debate-on-fine-line-between-freedom-of-expression-and-incitement-of-hatred%2Farticleshow%2F103354535.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Opposition%20Stands%20to%20Gain%20More%20From%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Move%20to%20Unify%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposing%20any%20decision%20that%20has%20been%20sprung%20on%20a%20country%20by%20its%20government%20without%20prior%20discussion%20is%20a%20reflex%20action%20among%20opposition%20parties%20in%20all%20democracies.%20So%20it%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise%20that%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Choudhury%2C%20the%20only%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20whom%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20invited%20to%20join%20the%20eight%20member%20panel%20that%20it%20is%20setting%20up%2C%20ostensibly%20to%20study%20but%20in%20reality%20to%20whitewash%2C%20the%20re-unification%20of%20central%20and%20state%20elections%2C%20has%20refused%20to%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDivorced%20from%20its%20present%20political%20context%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20not%20welcome%20the%20proposal%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections.%20The%20move%20will%20halve%20the%20presently%20crippling%20electioneering%20expenses%20for%20political%20parties.%20And%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20need%20to%20raise%20money%2C%20much%20of%20which%20has%20been%20coming%20from%20clandestine%20and%20criminal%20sources%20ever%20since%20the%20ban%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20put%20on%20company%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20in%201970.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReunification%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20also%20make%20it%20far%20easier%20for%20a%20future%20government%20to%20set%20up%20a%20state%20financed%20and%20publicly%20audited%20system%20of%20election%20financing.%20This%20would%20not%20only%20weaken%20and%2C%20over%20time%2C%20eliminate%20the%20nexus%20between%20crime%20and%20politics%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20also%20open%20the%20way%20for%20reforms%20in%20the%20police%20and%20lower%20administration%20that%20will%20cleanse%20the%20government%20of%20corruption%20and%20make%20it%20serve%20the%20people.%20It%20would%20also%20lengthen%20the%20time%20horizon%20over%20which%20government%20policies%20will%20need%20to%20bear%20fruit%3B%20restore%20the%20Centre-State%20co-ordination%20in%20policy%20making%20that%20was%20severely%20weakened%20by%20the%20separation%20of%20central%20from%20state%20elections%2C%20and%20facilitate%20structural%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felections-2024-india-most-dangerous-phase%5C%22%3EAs%20the%202024%20Elections%20Approach%2C%20India%20Is%20Entering%20the%20Most%20Dangerous%20Phase%20of%20Its%20Existence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20enacted%20with%20necessary%20safeguards%2C%20it%20will%20also%20put%20a%20brake%20on%20opportunistic%20defections%20from%20political%20parties.%20The%20most%20necessary%20of%20these%20safeguards%20will%20be%20an%20automatic%20declaration%20of%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20till%20the%20next%20general%20election%20in%20any%20state%20where%20the%20government%20has%20been%20brought%20down%20by%20defections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20reasons%20for%20taking%20this%20sudden%20decision%2C%20however%2C%20have%20little%20to%20do%20with%20better%20governance.%20He%20has%20taken%20it%20because%20he%20is%20aware%20that%20the%20BJP%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20suffering%20the%20same%20fate%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20possibly%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20that%20it%20suffered%20in%20Karnataka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20therefore%20understandably%20wary%20of%20going%20into%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20a%20string%20of%20electoral%20defeats%20in%20major%20states%20behind%20him.%20So%20he%20has%20decided%20to%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%20%E2%80%93%20avoid%20four%20important%20state%20elections%20that%20his%20party%20could%20lose%2C%20and%20hold%20a%20combined%20national%20and%20state%20election%20with%20the%20prestige%20of%20the%20G-20%20presidency%20and%20its%20grand%20conference%20in%20Delhi%20to%20buoy%20him%2C%20delivering%20both%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20state%20to%20his%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-election-fourth-committee%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%2C%20Fourth%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20INDIA%20coalition%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20one-election%20proposal%20is%20therefore%20understandable.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20short-sighted%20because%20unifying%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20will%20resolve%20the%20most%20knotty%20problem%20that%20the%20alliance%20is%20facing%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20next%20general%20election%20and%20greatly%20improve%20its%20chances%20of%20victory.%20This%20problem%20is%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20to%20its%20constituent%20parties%20in%20each%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%20showed%2C%20the%20coalition%20is%20determined%20to%20field%20only%20one%20candidate%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20each%20constituency.%20But%20it%20has%20yet%20to%20decide%20from%20which%20party%2C%20and%20on%20what%20basis%20the%20candidate%20should%20be%20chosen.%20At%20the%20Patna%20meeting%2C%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamta%20Bannerjee%20had%20told%20the%20press%20that%20the%20alliance%20would%20set%20up%20coordination%20committees%20that%20would%20first%20decide%20the%20principles%20they%20would%20follow%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20and%20then%20use%20these%20to%20choose%20the%20party%20and%20candidate%20for%20each%20constituency.%20Today%2C%20two%20more%20alliance%20meetings%20later%2C%20that%20process%20is%20only%20about%20to%20begin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20foot-dragging%20is%20taking%20place%20because%20the%20party%20leaders%20have%20not%20found%20a%20way%20to%20cross%20the%20main%20hurdle%20they%20face%3A%20how%20to%20retain%20the%20loyalty%20and%20support%20of%20their%20cadres%20in%20the%20constituencies%20that%20they%20have%20ceded%20to%20an%20ally%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20problem%20would%20not%20have%20arisen%20if%20there%20had%20been%20a%20system%20of%20state%20financing%20of%20elections%20like%20the%20one%20Western%20Europe.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20parties%20have%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20local%20financiers%20whom%20they%20offer%20government%20contracts%20and%20other%20favours%20if%20their%20party%20comes%20to%20power.%20This%20clientelist%20system%20starts%20breaking%20down%20if%20the%20financiers%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20party%2C%20or%20in%20its%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20to%20win.%20It%20ceases%20to%20exist%20when%20the%20party%20has%20no%20horse%20in%20the%20race.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20offering%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20Modi%20has%20unwittingly%20offered%20INDIA%20a%20way%20out%20of%20its%20dilemma.%20This%20would%20confine%20the%20seat%20sharing%20between%20political%20parties%20only%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20allow%20full%20competition%20to%20continue%20between%20them%20sin%20the%20various%20state%20assemblies%20and%20also%20require%20them%20to%20make%20a%20clear%20demarcation%20between%20national%20and%20local%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParty%20cadres%20can%20then%20be%20instructed%20to%20emphasise%20national%20issues%20in%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20where%20their%20party%20is%20fielding%20candidates%20for%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%2C%20and%20to%20place%20greater%20stress%20on%20state%20and%20local%20issues%20in%20those%20where%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20has%20been%20allotted%20to%20another%20member%20of%20the%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprem-shankar-jha%5C%22%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-stands-to-gain-more-from-modis-move-to-unify-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20offering%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections%2C%20Modi%20has%20unwittingly%20offered%20INDIA%20a%20way%20out%20of%20its%20seat-sharing%20dilemma.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-stands-to-gain-more-from-modis-move-to-unify-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Political%20Ethics%20of%20the%20Indian%20Political%20Right%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F09155320%2FIMG_0444.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20challenge%20in%20recognising%2C%20realising%2C%20and%20endorsing%20place%20of%20emotions%20is%20how%20they%20do%20not%20become%20templates%20for%20righteous%20lawlessness%20and%20majoritarianism%E2%80%A6Emotive%20majority%20today%20is%20an%20undeniable%20reality%20in%20most%20of%20the%20world%2C%20but%20the%20consequences%20and%20the%20way%20they%20can%20be%20nudged%20towards%20compassionate%20cohabitation%20is%20still%20an%20open%20question.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20these%20words%2C%20political%20theorist%20Ajay%20Gudavarthy%2C%20in%20his%20recent%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPolitics%2C%20Ethics%20and%20Emotions%20in%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20attempts%20to%20unpack%20the%20moral%2C%20ethical%2C%20and%20emotive%20questions%20that%20may%20help%20one%20understand%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20political%20right%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20questions%20may%20also%20interest%20us%20in%20the%20current%20global%20context%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20rightwing%20conservatism%2C%20while%20studying%20how%20people%20cutting%20across%20castes%20and%20classes%20perceive%20the%20rightwing%20construct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20364px)%2085vw%2C%20364px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02170949%2F61Ux26RKqHL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22364%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02170949%2F61Ux26RKqHL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20654w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02170949%2F61Ux26RKqHL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-196x300.jpg%20196w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671188%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22557%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPolitics%2C%20Ethics%20and%20Emotions%20in%20%E2%80%98New%20India%2C%E2%80%99%20Ajay%20Gudavarthy%2C%20Routledge%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUsing%20a%20bio-political%20normative%20lens%2C%20the%20author%20puts%20forward%20a%20critical%20question%20in%20the%20book%3A%20%E2%80%9CHow%20do%20we%20remobilise%20and%20occupy%20ethics%20and%20emotions%20that%20are%20not%20majoritarian%2C%20ethics%20that%20do%20not%20eschew%20responsibility%2C%20and%20emotions%20that%20do%20not%20produce%20a%20valorised%20self%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Gudavarthy%2C%20this%20may%20be%20particularly%20relevant%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20contemporary%20political%20space%20and%20the%20everyday%20ethics%20of%20being%20in%20India%2C%20when%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20under%20Narendra%20Modi-Amit%20Shah%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cjustifiably%20mobilising%20emotions%20and%20striking%20a%20chord%20with%20a%20majority%2C%20but%20that%20is%20necessarily%20illiberal%20in%20nature%20and%20producing%20ethics%20that%20are%20blatantly%20majoritarian%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%E2%80%99s%20thesis%20is%20densely%20layered%20in%20three%20distinct%20parts%20(Part%20I%3A%20Politics%20and%20Emotions%2C%20Part%20II%3A%20Economy%20and%20Ethics%2C%20and%20Part%20III%3A%20Ethical%20Emotions%3F)%20and%20has%20been%20written%20in%20contribution%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98Reshaping%20India%E2%80%99%20book%20series%20produced%20by%20the%20Samruddha%20Bharat%20Foundation%20with%20Routledge%2C%20Taylor%20and%20Francis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20those%20reading%20Gudavarthy%E2%80%99s%20work%20for%20the%20first%20time%20may%20find%20more%20contextual%20meaning%20to%20this%20text%20after%20perceiving%20this%20as%20a%20sequel%20to%20his%20previous%20offering%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20After%20Modi%3A%20Populism%20and%20the%20Right%20(2018).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20missing%20woods%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20its%20initial%20background%20and%20interest%20is%20situated%20in%20studying%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20political%20%3Cem%3Er%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Eight%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ei.e.%20the%20BJP%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Modi-Shah%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Egovernmentality%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20in%20explaining%20their%20regime%E2%80%99s%20complex%20experiments%20with%20the%20everyday%20political%20ethics%20of%20being%20built%20around%20the%20tradecraft%20of%20seducing%20the%20emotive%20majority.%20This%20can%20perhaps%20help%20one%20explain%20a%20persistent%20rise%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20own%20popularity%2C%20accentuated%20by%20the%20emotive%20politics%20of%20thoughtless%20belief.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20interesting%20aspect%20of%20viewing%20the%20%E2%80%98emotive%E2%80%99%20influence%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20amongst%20the%20larger%20Indian%20electorate%20(especially%20the%20Hindi%20belt)%20despite%20the%20nature%20of%20social%20or%20economic%20issues%20that%20afflict%20the%20same%20majority%2C%20according%20to%20Gudavarthy%2C%20is%20established%20by%20understanding%20what%20the%20right%20invests%20is%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emorality%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20what%20a%20majority%20works%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20everyday%20ethics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20quote%20from%20Brent%20Adkins%20(below)%20is%20particularly%20striking%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20morality%20functions%20according%20to%20principle%20while%20an%20ethics%20functions%20according%20to%20experimentation.%20A%20morality%20presupposes%20a%20discontinuity%20between%20principle%20and%20action%2C%20while%20an%20ethics%20presupposes%20a%20continuity%20of%20action%20and%20character.%20A%20morality%20tells%20one%20what%20one%20ought%20to%20do%2C%20while%20an%20ethics%20asks%20what%20one%20might%20do%E2%80%9D%20(Brent%20Adkins%2C%202015%3B%20p147)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%2C%20somewhere%2C%20in%20the%20complex%20oscillations%20of%20a%20layered%20thesis%20that%20attempts%20to%20deal%20in%20ethics%2C%20morality%2C%20and%20emotions%2C%20all%20at%20once%2C%20there%20are%20voids%20and%20silences%20that%20emerge%20in%20Gudavarthy%E2%80%99s%20thesis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20everyday%20ethics%20of%20being%20and%20what%20may%20help%20explain%20the%20average%20Hindu%20voter%E2%80%99s%20(as%20part%20of%20the%20seduced%20emotive%20majority)%20motivational%20rationality%20can%20be%20studied%20by%20viewing%20the%20application%20of%20Dharma%2C%20Dharam%2C%20Kama%2C%20Karma.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Brahmanical%20cloak%20designed%20to%20guide%20each%20of%20these%20has%20been%20deeply%20politicised%20by%20the%20Modi-Shah-RSS%20regime%20which%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20establish%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20considers%20a%20persistent%20effort%20to%20influence%20these%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98emotive%20(Hindu)%20majority%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%20thus%20allows%20one%20to%20%E2%80%98clean%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98teach%20minorities%20a%20lesson%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20establish%20a%20masculine%20muscularity%20in%20a%20hyper-nationalist%20wave.%20It%20is%20all%20part%20of%20a%20political%20project%20that%20builds%20itself%20on%20a%20new%20morality%2C%20the%20ethics%20of%20being%20for%20emotions%20(rage%2C%20anger%2C%20violence)%20to%20be%20experienced%20and%20realised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20book%E2%80%99s%20normative%20axis%20misses%20in%20presenting%20a%20robust%20critique%20of%20liberal%20foundations%20and%20principles%20%E2%80%93%20that%20maybe%20less%20relevant%20for%20the%20Indian%20polity%20or%20society%20%E2%80%93%20is%20there%20is%20more%20left%20to%20be%20said%20on%20what%20drives%20a%20foundational%20link%20between%20the%20interplay%20of%20Morality-Ethics-Emotions%20(MEE)%20with%20the%20governing%20dynamics%20of%20Dharam%2C%20Dharma%2C%20Kama%20and%20Karma.%20The%20latter%20defines%20India%E2%80%99s%20socio-political%20landscape%20underplayed%20by%20a%20theory%20of%20power%2C%20faith%2C%20cultural%20propriety%2C%20memory%20and%20language.%20All%20of%20these%2C%20in%20some%20way%20or%20another%2C%20shape%20the%20everyday%20political%20ethics%20of%20being%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emajority%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20non-emotive%20here%20also%20entwine%20with%20the%20emotive%20class%2C%20while%20working%20as%20templates%20of%20self-representation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20empirical%20void%20that%20extrapolates%20from%20the%20normative%20void%20is%20the%20weak%20link%20drawn%20between%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20political%20r%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eight%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20narrativising%20an%20alternative%20%E2%80%98truth%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20satiated%20need%20of%20the%20emotive%20majority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20a%20majority%20will%20forget%20the%20acquired%20knowledge%20of%20the%20past%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98new%E2%80%99%20truth%20to%20be%20discovered.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20right%20has%20a%20complex%20techno-political%20relationship%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewith%20the%20contemporary%20tools%20and%20mechanisms%20of%20the%20current%20information%20order%20and%20digital%20technological%20infrastructure.%20It%20is%20the%20same%20structure%20that%20the%20right%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eweaponises%20on%20day-to-day%20basis.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENormative%20vision%20and%20ideas%20of%20ethics%20or%20morality%20are%20mediated%20through%20symbolism%20that%20can%20be%20manipulated%20through%20media%20and%20information%20flow.%20This%20has%20been%20most%20vital%20for%20the%20Modi-Shah%20double%20engine%20to%20not%20just%20acquire%20power%2C%20but%20also%20consolidate%20it%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBuilding%20the%20thesis%20forward%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FStrongmen-Saviours-A-Political-Economy-of-Populism-in-India-Turkey-Russia%2FMohan-Padmanabhan%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032288314%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EStrongmen%20Saviours%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20Abhinav%20Padmanabhan%2C%20our%20own%20comparative%20analysis%20of%20the%20recent%20wave%20of%20rightwing%20populist%20movements%20across%20the%20world%20was%20explained%20through%20a%20distinct%20pattern%20exhibiting%20features%20that%20have%20been%20unique%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20right-wing%20movements%20(as%20against%20left-wing%20movements%20of%20the%20past).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20purpose%20then%20was%20to%20provide%20a%20comparative%20socio-political%2C%20economic%20explanation%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20populist%20beliefs%20and%20anti-political%20elite%20sentiment%20that%20has%20not%20captured%20much%20of%20the%20Western%20and%20non-Western%20sphere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20pyramid%20constructed%20below%2C%20drawn-built%20on%20our%20book%E2%80%99s%20research%20may%20offer%20some%20insights%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02213823%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-9.38.04-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02213823%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-9.38.04-PM.png%20956w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02213823%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-9.38.04-PM-300x190.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671216%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22425%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conceptual%20pyramid%20attempts%20to%20unpack%20features%20of%20right-wing%20populism%2C%20operating%20under%20the%20guise-envelope%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FStrongmen-Saviours-A-Political-Economy-of-Populism-in-India-Turkey-Russia%2FMohan-Padmanabhan%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032288314%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98ideological%20populism%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(ideologically%20aligned%20populist%20movements)%2C%20which%20has%20a%20distinct%20meaning%20(see%20a%20more%20detailed%20explainer%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Flive%2FPgPnQ3RmdqA%3Ffeature%3Dshare%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20simple%20terms%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eideological%20populism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0refers%20to%20the%20unchecked-unabated%20rise%20of%20an%20ideology%2C%20the%20marginalization%20of%20its%20moderate%20factions%2C%20involving%20the%20development%20of%20a%20cult-personality%20that%20infuses%20shades%20of%20populism%20into%20it.%20Normatively%2C%20this%20can%20be%20ideologically%20aligned%20towards%20the%20%E2%80%98political%20left%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98political%20right%E2%80%99.%20The%20distinct%20characteristics%20of%20rightwing%20populism%20at%20least%20the%20way%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FStrongmen-Saviours-A-Political-Economy-of-Populism-in-India-Turkey-Russia%2FMohan-Padmanabhan%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032288314%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewe%20have%20observed%20in%20countries%20such%20as%20India%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20Brazil%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edid%20see%20certain%20common%20features%2C%20across%20different%20times%20and%20spaces.%20I%20explained%20a%20few%20of%20these%20factors%2Ffeatures%20from%20the%20pyramid%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fright-wing-populism-towards-a-new-theory-of-economic-change%23read-more%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20factors%20contribute%20to%20the%20right%E2%80%99s%20authoritative%20rise%20to%20majoritarian%20power.%20They%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFailure%20of%20Neoliberalism%20(supply-side%20economics%20of%20the%2090s)%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20origins%20of%20each%20of%20these%20movements%20are%20in%20the%20economic%20discontents%20of%20neoliberalism%20or%20the%20nature%20of%20supply-side%20economics%20(externally%20influenced%20by%20the%20West%2FWashington%20Consensus%20style%20reform%20packages)%20pursued%20in%20the%201990s.%20Studies%20from%20scholars%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESides%20et%20al.%20(2018)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENorris%20%26amp%3B%20Inglehart%20(2019)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMargalit%20(2019)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0also%20explain%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20wave%20of%20rise%20in%20religious%20conservatism%20or%20religious%20orthodoxy%20(from%20Hindutva%20to%20Orthodox%20Islam%20to%20Evangelical%20Catholicism)%20that%20aided%20the%20rise%20of%20each%20of%20the%20leaders%20who%20either%20belonged%20to%20political%20parties%20or%20to%20orthodox-religious%20based%20organisations%20which%20ensured%20an%20undercurrent%20of%20religious%20conservatism.%20This%20made%20more%20people%20open%20to%20acknowledging%2C%20practicing%20or%20promoting%20%E2%80%98extreme%E2%80%99%20beliefs.%20I%20explain%20more%20about%20this%20phenomenon%20(as%20seen%20in%20India%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20Brazil)%20in%20a%20lecture%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Flive%2FPgPnQ3RmdqA%3Ffeature%3Dshare%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egiven%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trigger%20factor%20which%20led%20to%20the%20mass-protest%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20each%20strongman%20figure%20from%20Modi%20to%20Bolsonaro%2C%20was%20often%20related%20to%20either%20a%20series%20of%20big%20public%20corruption%20episodes%20or%20reported%20scandal(s)%20in%20the%20home%20country%E2%80%99s%20domestic%20political%20environment%2C%20which%20gave%20the%20opportunity%20for%20mass%20support%20in%20favour%20of%20an%20alternative%20imagination%20of%20power.%20A%20leader%2C%20someone%20outside%20the%20status%20quo%20ruling%20political%20elite%2C%20came%20to%20power%2C%20and%20enjoyed%20mass%20popularity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20India%20to%20Brazil%2C%20each%20of%20the%20countries%20we%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ediscuss%20in%20the%20book%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20saw%20episodes%20of%20public%20corruption%20via%20scandals%20or%20were%20operating%20in%20a%20widely%20perceived%20environment%20of%20corruption%20that%20spurred%20the%20choice%20of%20voting%20for%20an%20alternative.%20This%20was%20also%20seen%20with%20the%20protest%20vote%20for%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20the%202016%20US%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20weaponisation%20of%20social%20media%20in%20a%20new%20tech-enabled%20information%20order%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20rightwing%20populists%20to%20continue%20feeding%20an%20alternative%2C%20post-truth%20rhetorical%20narrative%20of%20%E2%80%98us%20versus%20them%E2%80%99%2C%20pivoted%20on%20the%20axis%20of%20immigration.%20Surveillance%20capitalism%20made%20this%20possible%20too%20under%20a%20new%20nexus%20of%20private%20capital-state%20relationship%20which%20supported%20strongmen%20figures%20in%20power%20through%20social%20media%20and%20digitised%20surveillance%20tools.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFocus%20on%20privatisation%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nature%20of%20fiscal%20policy%20brought%20by%20each%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eright-wing%20populist%20strongman%20figures%20in%20recent%20years%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20been%20drastically%20varied%20when%20compared%20to%20earlier%20regimes%20of%20populist%20movements%20(as%20seen%20in%20Latin%20America).%20Earlier%20strongman%20leaderships%20were%20influenced%20by%20a%20theory%20of%20economic%20and%20political%20change%20belonging%20to%20pro-welfare%2C%20left-leaning%20policies%2C%20which%20in%20some%20instances%20like%20Venezuela%20made%20governments%20fiscally%20indebted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20latest%20variant%20of%20rightwing%20populism%20has%20seen%20a%20promotion%20of%20privatisation%20and%20reorientation%20of%20previous%20state-private%20capital%20elite%20relationships.%20This%20has%20been%20pursued%20with%20gradual%20disinvestment%20of%20public%20assets%20and%20government%20ownership%20of%20resources%2C%20including%20a%20de-funding%20of%20social%20programmes%20targeted%20for%20job%20creation%2C%20human%20capital%20development-healthcare%20and%20education.%20This%20is%20widely%20seen%20in%20the%20fiscal%20choices%20made%20by%20most%20strongman%20figures%20like%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20strongmen%20continue%20to%20strike%20a%20chord%20with%20extremely%20low-income%20voters%20in%20some%20of%20the%20lesser%20developed%20states%20and%20provinces%20thanks%20to%20the%20political%20use%20of%20targeted%20beneficiary-based%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20must%20however%20be%20observed%20that%20none%20of%20this%20so-called%20welfare%20spending%20is%20aimed%20at%20the%20upward%20mobility%20of%20the%20low-income%20beneficiary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOn%20contestations%20within%3A%20Hyper-globalism%20and%20ideological%20populism%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDani%20Rodrik%E2%80%99s%20recent%20work%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.annualreviews.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1146%2Fannurev-economics-070220-032416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrodrik.scholar.harvard.edu%2Fsites%2Fscholar.harvard.edu%2Ffiles%2Fdani-rodrik%2Ffiles%2Fon_productivism.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E)%20offers%20useful%20insights%20on%20at%20least%20addressing%20one%20of%20these%20%E2%80%98contested%E2%80%99%20conceptual%20questions%3A%20Why%20did%20globalisation%20of%20the%20post-1990s%20variant%20fuel%20a%20certain%20wave%20of%20populism%2C%20one%20that%20spread%20far%20across%20the%20west%20and%20the%20east%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Rodrik%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20what%20are%20the%20mechanisms%20through%20which%20globalisation%20fuels%20populism.%20Answering%20this%20question%20requires%20a%20fully%20fleshed-out%20model%20of%20political%20economy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20globalisation%20is%20not%20just%20one%20thing.%20We%20can%20distinguish%20between%20international%20trade%2C%20international%20finance%2C%20and%20international%20labour%20flows%2C%20specifically.%20How%20does%20each%20one%20of%20these%20facets%20of%20globalisation%20work%20its%20way%20through%20the%20political%20system%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThird%2C%20globalisation%20is%20clearly%20not%20the%20only%20economic%20shock%20that%20creates%20redistributive%20effects%20or%20economic%20anxiety%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it%20may%20not%20even%20be%20the%20most%20important%20one.%20Why%20does%20globalisation%20appear%20to%20have%20an%20outsized%20effect%20on%20politics%20compared%20to%2C%20say%2C%20technological%20change%20or%20regular%20business%20cycles%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20aspects%20are%20studied%20more%20empirically%20by%20Rodrik%20in%20the%20framework%20created%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04155427%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.51.45.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22694%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04155427%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.51.45.png%20912w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04155427%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-3.51.45-300x256.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22592%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20according%20to%20Rodrik%E2%80%99s%20analytical%20framework%20above%2C%20and%20most%20directly%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeconomic%20dislocation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0can%20determine%20voters%E2%80%99%20preferences%20for%20policies%20and%20leaders%20(arrow%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20Voters%20in%20a%20region%20where%20employment%20prospects%20have%20been%20adversely%20affected%20by%20a%20rise%20in%20imports%20may%20choose%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%20for%20a%20politician%20who%20advocates%20protectionism%20and%20a%20tougher%20line%20against%20foreign%20exporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20economic%20dislocation%20may%20shape%20voters%E2%80%99%20preferences%20indirectly%20through%20the%20effect%20it%20has%20on%20identity%20or%20the%20salience%20of%20certain%20cultural%20values%20(arrow%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eb%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E).%20Concretely%2C%20economic%20shocks%20can%20heighten%20feelings%20of%20insecurity%2C%20inducing%20voters%20to%20make%20sharper%20distinctions%20between%20insiders%20(%E2%80%9Cus%E2%80%9D)%20and%20ethnic%2C%20religious%2C%20or%20racial%20outsiders%20(%E2%80%9Cthem%E2%80%9D).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20can%20lead%20voters%20to%20yearn%20for%20an%20earlier%20era%20of%20prosperity%20and%20stability%2C%20increasing%20the%20political%20salience%20of%20traditional%20cultural%20values%20and%20hierarchies.%20And%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20generate%20wider%20economic%20and%20social%20gaps%20within%20a%20nation%2C%20economic%20shocks%20may%20reinforce%20more%20local%2C%20less%20encompassing%20identities.%20To%20the%20extent%20that%20such%20effects%20operate%2C%20political%20preferences%20that%20appear%20to%20be%20driven%20by%20cultural%20values%20do%20in%20fact%20have%20deeper%20economic%20roots.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FStrongmen-Saviours-A-Political-Economy-of-Populism-in-India-Turkey-Russia%2FMohan-Padmanabhan%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032288314%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexplored%20some%20of%20these%20links%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20the%20discontents%20of%20neoliberal%20economics%20and%20populism%20in%20the%20context%20of%20India%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20Russia%2C%20however%2C%20there%20were%20other%20factors%20complementing%20this%20and%20Rodrik%E2%80%99s%20framework%20shared%20above.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20additional%20causal%20factors%20are%20instances%20of%20large-scale%20public%20corruption%20(or%20an%20environment%20of%20an%20ostensibly%20corrupt%20political%20elite)%2C%20and%20a%20rise%20in%20religious%20conservatism%20contributed%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20rightwing%20populist%20movements%20that%20subsequently%20brought%20leaders%20like%20Modi%2C%20Bolsonaro%2C%20and%20Putin%2C%20to%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20critical%20need%20to%20put%20these%20explanations%20in%20perspective%20and%20context%20while%20building%20upon%20what%20Gudavarthy%E2%80%99s%20frame%20of%20reasoning%20brings%20in%20light.%20This%20must%20be%20done%20by%20adopting%20a%20more%20neo-subaltern%20approach%20that%20is%20grounded%20in%20interpreting%20a%20random%20person%E2%80%99s%20preference%20for%20the%20political%20right.%20One%20must%20also%20see%20how%20the%20right%20operates%20in%20influencing%20one%E2%80%99s%20everyday%20ethics%20distinctively%20and%20assertively%2C%20while%20thriving%20on%20the%20anxieties%2C%20fears%2C%20and%20insecurities%20of%20the%20emotive%20majority.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20more%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20in%20also%20understanding%20how%20the%20moral-ethical%20core%20of%20an%20average%20Hindu%20voter%20subscribing%20to%20the%20populist%20belief%20remains%20influenced%20by%20the%20applied%20role%20of%20Dharam%2C%20Dharma%2C%20Kama%20and%20Karma%20in%20everyday%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20an%20associate%20professor%20and%20director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%20at%20O.P.%20Jindal%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https