93%20the%20physical%20victimisation%20of%20women%20is%20a%20problem%20that%20needs%20urgent%20attention.%20While%20comprehensive%20social%20reform%20which%20ensures%20access%20to%20education%20and%20healthcare%2C%20equal%20livelihood%20opportunities%20and%20equal%20wages%20is%20required%20to%20arrest%20the%20ever-rising%20incidence%20of%20violence%20against%20women%2C%20a%20well-thought-out%20prevention%2C%20protection%20and%20empowerment%20mechanism%20should%20also%20be%20in%20place%20to%20stop%20such%20incidents.%20The%20political%20will%20of%20the%20government%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20there%20have%20been%20a%20couple%20of%20government%20interventions%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20violence%20against%20women.%20It%20is%20instructive%20to%20analyse%20how%20these%20schemes%20have%20been%20prioritised%20by%20the%20current%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013-14%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20set%20up%20a%20non-lapsable%20corpus%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%20for%20special%20police%20helplines%2C%20safety%20in%20transportation%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013-14%2C%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20was%20allocated%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%20fund%2C%20which%20was%20then%20reduced%20to%20Rs%20550%20crore%20in%202017-18%2C%202018-19%2C%20and%202019-20.%20It%20was%20further%20reduced%20to%20around%20Rs%20500%20crore%20in%202021-22%20and%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20utilisation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%20fund%20is%20also%20very%20poor.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F164.100.77.118%2Fview_detail%2FeyJpdiI6IjFtY3I3cUdYbVVpMG1Lb2tpdnk5SkE9PSIsInZhbHVlIjoiNFZ1Wlp0Mmphb2xpVmpvckVxZk1mdz09IiwibWFjIjoiZTdmZjllYjQ2NmJiNGQyZjM3ZmY1YmIxY2ZiYWQwMWE5MTJlOTljYTI3ZDc1NGIwN2YyNDJjMTBmNmExOTJlNiJ9%5C%22%3EAs%20on%20April%2028%2C%202023%2C%20around%20Rs%2012%2C008.5%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20appraised%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%2