guard%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20his%20office%20after%20failing%20to%20secure%20an%20appointment%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20urged%20governor%20C.P.%20Radhakrishnan%20to%20send%20observations%20on%20three%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20bills%E2%80%9D%20that%20had%20been%20returned%20by%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20emailed%20and%20also%20given%20a%20letter%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%20on%20Friday%20%5BSeptember%201%5D%20seeking%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20governor%20on%20Sunday%20%5BSeptember%203%5D.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20one%20available%20at%20the%20office%20and%20we%20had%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20memorandum%20at%20the%20gate%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vinod%20Pandey%2C%20an%20SSC%20member%20and%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20meet%20the%20governor%20and%20apprise%20him%20about%20the%20three%20important%20bills%20%E2%80%93%201932%20Khatiyan%20(land%20survey)%20based%20definition%20of%20locals%20bill%2C%20the%20anti-lynching%20bill%20and%20the%20bill%20pertaining%20to%20raising%20the%20reservation%20quota%20of%20OBC%20communities.%20All%20these%20bills%20had%20been%20returned%20by%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20without%20sending%20the%20necessary%20observations%20of%20the%20governor%20(both%20former%20governor%20Ramesh%20Bais%20and%20incumbent%20C.P.%20Radhakrishnan).%20We%20want%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20to%20send%20the%20observations%20so%20that%20the%20necessary%20corrections%20can%20be%20done%20and%20reintroduced%20in%20the%20Assembly%20and%20send%20it%20again%20to%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCC%20members%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F04%2Fjharkhand-ruling-alliance-members-submit-memo-to-governors-guard-on-3-bills-2611490.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20has%20not%20mentioned%20the%20specific%20objections%20in%20the%20Bills%2C%20violating%20Article%20200%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SSC%20has%20been%20formed%20by%20the%20three%20ruling%20ally%20parties%20in%20Jharkhand%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20and%20JMM.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Radhakrishnan%20is%20a%20former%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20and%20has%20also%20served%20as%20the%20BJP%20state%20president%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20accused%20the%20governor%20of%20working%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20%E2%80%9Ca%20particular%20party%20or%20person%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20(TNIE)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F04%2Fjharkhand-ruling-alliance-members-submit-memo-to-governors-guard-on-3-bills-2611490.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20the%20governor%20does%20not%20want%20local%20and%20reservation%20policies%20to%20be%20formulated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandey%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETNIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%20They%20want%20the%20governor%20to%20clear%20his%20stand%20on%20the%20three%20bills%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20Assembly%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20chief%20Rajesh%20Thakur%20said%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20are%20not%20given%20time%20by%20the%20Raj%20Bhawan.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20freely%20enter%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20set%20their%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thakur%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3ETNIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20secretariat%20had%20in%20July%20issued%20a%20communique%20detailing%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intent%20to%20reintroduce%20the%20three%20bills%20and%20their%20request%20to%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20secretariat%20to%20forward%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20governor%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBills%20passed%20by%20the%20Assembly%20are%20sent%20to%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20for%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20assent.%20The%20copy%20of%20the%20bills%20consists%20of%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20observations%20in%20case%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20consents%20to%20them%20or%20has%20some%20objections.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20these%20bills%2C%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20observations%20are%20missing.%20Since%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20re-introduce%20the%20bills%2C%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20observations%20have%20been%20sought%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Eread%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20Definition%20for%20Local%20Persons%20and%20for%20Extending%20Consequential%2C%20Social%2C%20Cultural%20and%20Other%20Benefits%20to%20Such%20Local%20Persons%20Bill%20of%202022%20set%20the%20land%20survey%20settlements%20of%201932%20as%20the%20benchmark%20for%20identifying%20the%20locals%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20bill%20was%20passed%20in%20an%20extended%20monsoon%20session%20last%20year%2C%20but%20returned%20by%20the%20then%20governor%20Ramesh%20Bais%20stating%20that%20it%20violated%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20(Prevention%20of%20Violence%20and%20Mob%20Lynching)%20Bill%20of%202021%2C%20passed%20in%20the%20winter%20session%20of%202021%2C%20was%20returned%20by%20Bais%20seeking%20clarity%20on%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%98mob%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20OBC%20reservation%20bill%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20increase%20reservations%20for%20OBC%20communities%20to%2027%25%20from%2014%25%20was%20returned%20by%20Radhakrishnan%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20receiving%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20holds%20significance%20as%20these%20issues%20have%20been%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20government%E2%80%99s%20political%20narrative%20besides%20being%20electoral%20promises%20in%20the%202019%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693816248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04123209%2FF48K1wDXgAAyXu7.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjharkand-government-hands-memo-for-governor-to-raj-bhawan-security-after-failing-to-get-appointment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20memorandum%20urged%20governor%20C.P.%20Radhakrishnan%20to%20send%20observations%20on%20three%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20bills%E2%80%9D%20which%20had%20been%20returned%20by%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjharkand-government-hands-memo-for-governor-to-raj-bhawan-security-after-failing-to-get-appointment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20a%20Record%20Dry%20August%2C%20Is%20India's%20Kharif%20Harvest%20in%20Trouble%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%