3E%20and%20other%20custom%20duties%20on%20vegetables%20and%20other%20food%20products%20clear%20point%20to%20another%20reality.%20Our%20policy%20makers%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20imminent%20food%20crisis.%20If%20its%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20rain%20as%20expected%20in%20September%2C%20the%20rain-fed%20areas%20will%20undergo%20deep%20hardship%2C%20increasing%20pressure%20on%20the%20government.%20The%20people%20with%20irrigation%20options%20or%20%E2%80%9Cunderground%20boring%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20the%20ever-shrinking%20surface%20and%20ground%20water%20resources.%20Because%20there%20is%20no%20way%20the%20farmers%20or%20the%20government%20can%20afford%20another%20below%20average%20harvest.%20The%20Rabi%20harvests%20have%20been%20below%20average%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years%20now.%20Kharif%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20the%20best%20either.%20Untimely%20rainfall%2C%20heatwaves%20and%20hailstorms%20have%20done%20the%20most%20damage%20across%20the%20subcontinent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20food%20stocks%20have%20already%20depleted%20and%20many%20police%20makers%20and%20farmers%20were%20hoping%20for%20a%20good%20harvest%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20nature%20has%20other%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgro-climatic%20crisis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20zoom%20out%20a%20bit%2C%20and%20ask%20certain%20questions%3A%20What%20has%20been%20happening%20to%20India%3F%20Are%20things%20really%20changing%20agriculturally%3F%20Are%20we%20headed%20into%20a%20food%20crisis%3F%20The%20short%20answer%20to%20the%20last%20two%20questions%2C%20from%20everything%20we%20know%20so%20far%2C%20is%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20agro-climate%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20prolonged%20climate%20agrarian%20disruptions%20%E2%80%93%20became%20visible%20in%202019%2C%20with%20disrupted%20monsoons%2C%20floods%20and%20eight%20tropical%20cyclones.%20As%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-seventh-most-affected-by-climate-change-in-2019-globally-report-101611552192319.html%5C%22%3Eglobal%20report%20on%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20the%20seventh%20most-affected%20by%20the%20devastating%20impact%20of%20climate%20change%20globally%20in%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20changing%20climate%20eating%20as%20much%20as%200.72%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20wound%20was%20the%20unusual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Flocust-attack-india-jaipur-climate-change%5C%22%3E2020%20locust%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20reportedly%20the%20biggest%20such%20attack%20in%20over%20three%20decades.%20Locusts%20damaged%20crops%20all%20across%20the%20western%20and%20northern%20subcontinent.%20The%20untimely%20rainfall%20provided%20new%20breeding%20grounds%20for%20locusts%20in%20western%20India.%20This%20was%20another%20symptom%20of%20the%20agro-climate%20crisis%20building%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Is%20Indian%20Agriculture%20Following%20Two%20Policies%20%E2%80%93%20One%20at%20WTO%20and%20Another%20at%20Home%3F%C2%A0%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmodi-agriculture-wto-msp-policies-niti-aayog%5C%22%3EIs%20Indian%20Agriculture%20Following%20Two%20Policies%20%E2%80%93%20One%20at%20WTO%20and%20Another%20at%20Home%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2021%20again%20showed%20untimely%20rainfalls%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1696515%5C%22%3EIMD%20pointed%20out%20six%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20receiving%20decreased%20rainfall%2C%20while%2012%20states%20had%20excessive%20rainfall.%20Overall%2C%20about%2040%25%20of%20the%20703%20districts%20in%20India%20had%20average%20rainfall.%20In%20six%20years%20(2015-21)%2C%20India%20lost%2033.9%20million%20hectares%20of%20crop%20land%20to%20floods%20and%20excess%20rains%20and%2035%20million%20hectares%20to%20drought%20%E2%80%93%20numbers%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20increase%20as%20years%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20we%20see%20the%20pattern%20re-emerging%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fheatwave-impact-wheat-yield-falls-by-13-5-in-punjab-101652211100645.html%5C%22%3Edampened%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rabi%20harvests%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy-heavy-rains-hit-kharif-crops-ahead-of-harvest-2706312%2F%5C%22%3Euntimely%3C%2Fa%3E%20kharif%20rains%20and%20kharif%20paddy%20production%20dropping%20by%206%25.%20Meanwhile%2C%20heat-related%20deaths%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1035871%2Fheat-related-deaths-in-india-increased-by-55-in-last-17-years-finds-lancet-study%5C%22%3Eincreased%20by%2055%25%20in%2017%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20victims%20were%20not%20just%20humans%2C%20but%20also%20the%20Rabi%20wheat%20crop%20in%20north%20India%2C%20which%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fheatwave-impact-wheat-yield-falls-by-13-5-in-punjab-101652211100645.html%5C%22%3Eshrank%20by%20at%20least%2013.5%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20government%20was%20quick%20to%20ban%20wheat%20exports%2C%20while%20trying%20to%20curtail%20public%20panic.%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20in%20her%20parliament%20address%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fagriculture-sector-needs-re-orientation-due-to-likely-hurdles-in-climate-change-surge-in-costs-of-inputs-8416255%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20(agriculture)%20grew%20by%203.0%25%20in%202021-22%20compared%20to%203.3%25%20in%202020-21%E2%80%9D%20and%20blamed%20the%20changing%20climate%20for%20it.%20She%20plainly%20also%20spelt%20out%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20%E2%80%9Cre-orient%E2%80%9D%20its%20policy%20to%20tackle%20the%20challenge%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20Punjab%20Agriculture%20University%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpunjab-likely-to-suffer-yield-loss-of-all-major-crops-by-2050-due-to-temp-rise-climate-study%2Farticleshow%2F97259650.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20concurs%20with%20the%20finance%20minister%E2%80%99s%20view%20and%20predicts%20that%20Punjab%20by%202050%20will%20be%20grappling%20with%20changing%20climate%20and%20experience%20significant%20yield%20loss%20due%20to%20rising%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022-23%20Rabi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkharif-rice-production-to-drop-by-6-agriculture-ministry-8165444%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20no%20different%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Different%20parts%20of%20India%20experience%20climatic%20issues%2C%20mainly%20untimely%20rainfall.%20Punjab%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20were%20affected.%20And%20then%20came%20Biparjoy%2C%20tearing%20into%20the%20western%20subcontinent%20and%20drying%20up%20our%20monsoons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20the%20second%2C%20economic%20phase%20of%20the%20agro-climatic%20crisis%20is%20reached%20%E2%80%93%20hyper%20food%20inflation.%20From%20tomatoes%20and%20onions%2C%20now%20the%20inflation%20is%20reaching%20other%20staples%20like%20legumes%20and%20vegetables.%20Fodder%20prices%20are%20increasing%20gradually%2C%20as%20the%20Indian%20system%20is%20losing%20its%20resilience%20because%20of%20climate%20disruptions.%20A%20majority%20of%20government%20schemes%20have%20failed%20to%20build%20infrastructure%20or%20freight%20networks%20for%20storage%20and%20preventing%20climate-related%20harvest%20damages.%20From%20hailstorms%20in%20Kashmir%20to%20a%20dry%20August%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20farmers%20are%20least%20prepared%2C%20and%20hence%20harvest%20losses%20will%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20our%20strategic%20food%20reserves%20are%20at%20their%20lowest%2C%20and%20800%20million%20are%20directly%20fed%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20public%20distribution%20system.%20With%20the%20rupee%20floating%20around%2082-83%20to%20the%20dollar%20and%20the%20Ukraine-Russia%20conflict%20still%20escalating%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20really%20depend%20on%20the%20international%20market%20for%20our%20food%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20third%20stage%20of%20the%20agro-climate%20food%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20the%20convergence%20phase.%20If%20the%20kharif%20harvest%20fails%20or%20is%20again%20below%20average%2C%20Indian%20food%20security%20will%20be%20deeply%20impacted%20due%20to%20the%20compounding%20of%20climate-related%20agrarian%20losses.%20We%20will%20be%20in%20the%20third%20stage%20of%20the%20crisis%20once%20the%20agriculture%20production%20is%20hampered%20and%20the%20economic%20measures%20fail%20to%20control%20hyper-food%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20or%20three%20cycles%20of%20this%20pattern%2C%20and%20any%20country%20is%20looking%20straight%20at%20a%20full%20blown%20agro-climate%20crisis.%20Bad%20harvests%2C%20repeated%20climate%20disruptions%2C%20hyper-food%20inflation%2C%20scarcity%20and%20no%20international%20supplies%20together%20are%20a%20malnutrition%20time%20bomb.%20If%20our%20agrarian%20trajectory%20is%20not%20changed%2C%202024%20or%202025%20maybe%20the%20years%20where%20a%20full%20nutritious%20meal%20is%20a%20privilege%20few%20can%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20is%20an%20independent%20agri-policy%20analyst%20and%20writer.%20He%20was%20the%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20NSAI.%20He%20also%20hosts%20The%20Wire%20agri-talk%20show%20%E2%80%98Krishi%20ki%20baat%2FFarm%20Talks%E2%80%99.%20He%20tweets%20on%20%40indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693816231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04102045%2F11835209326_7c1729bdf5_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fafter-a-record-dry-august-is-indias-kharif-harvest-in-trouble%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IMD%20may%20have%20predicted%20normal%20rainfall%20for%20September%2C%20but%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20aggressive%20ban%20on%20rice%20exports%20and%20other%20custom%20duties%20on%20vegetables%20and%20other%20food%20products%20clear%20point%20to%20another%20reality.%20Our%20policy%20makers%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20imminent%20food%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fafter-a-record-dry-august-is-indias-kharif-harvest-in-trouble%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Pakistani%20Military's%20Role%20in%20National%20Politics%20Is%20Growing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04135237%2Fgallery-image2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20army%20has%20been%20aptly%20described%20as%20a%20state%20within%20a%20state.%20It%20came%20to%20acquire%20a%20prime%20position%20in%20Pakistan%20from%20its%20early%20years%20for%20various%20reasons%3A%20absence%20of%20a%20civilian%20leader%20of%20stature%20after%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%3B%20Pakistan%20turning%20into%20a%20security%20state%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20rival%20India%3B%20preponderantly%20Punjabi%20army%20in%20the%20Punjab-dominated%20state%3B%20difficulties%20in%20framing%20the%20first%20constitution%20because%20of%20West%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20concede%20the%20democratic%20rights%20of%20the%20numerically%20superior%20eastern%20wing%3B%20and%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20alliance%20with%20the%20Western%20bloc%20with%20a%20leading%20role%20for%20the%20army%20and%20large%20flows%20of%20US%20assistance%20to%20it%20in%20cash%20and%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20army%20has%20ruled%20the%20state%20directly%20for%2033%20years%20and%20exercised%20influence%20from%20behind%20the%20scenes%20during%20the%20remaining%20period.%20It%20has%20shown%20resilience%20in%20recovering%20from%20periodic%20setbacks%2C%20including%20its%20crushing%20defeat%20in%201971%2C%20using%20strong-arm%20tactics%20and%20intimidation%20to%20enforce%20its%20will.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20came%20as%20a%20surprise%20when%20its%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%2C%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20revolted%20on%20being%20driven%20out%20of%20power%20in%202022%20after%20falling%20out%20with%20the%20former%20army%20chief%20Qamar%20Javed%20Bajwa%2C%20posing%20a%20challenge%20to%20Bajwa%20and%20his%20successor%2C%20Asim%20Munir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20time%2C%20it%20seemed%20that%20the%20army%20had%20finally%20come%20upon%20its%20comeuppance.%20The%20challenge%2C%20initially%20open%20criticism%20of%20the%20army%20leadership%2C%20took%20a%20violent%20turn%20after%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20on%20May%209%2C%202023.%20For%20two%20days%2C%20until%20his%20release%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20his%20supporters%20perpetrated%20violence%20of%20an%20unprecedented%20sweep%20and%20intensity%20against%20important%20military%20installations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fimran-khans-arrest-will-exacerbate-pakistans-multi-system-meltdown%5C%22%3EImran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20Arrest%20Will%20Exacerbate%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Multi-System%20Meltdown%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%20had%20clearly%20overplayed%20his%20hand.%20Asim%20Munir%20used%20the%20violence%20to%20consolidate%20his%20position.%20He%20obtained%20the%20support%20of%20his%20senior%20commanders%20and%20the%20civilian%20set-up%20to%20take%20strict%20action%20against%20the%20perpetrators%20and%20instigators%20of%20the%20violence%2C%20including%20through%20trials%20in%20military%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20action%20against%20a%20number%20of%20senior%20army%20officers%20sympathetic%20to%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20including%20the%20dismissal%20of%20a%20Lieutenant%20General.%20Many%20senior%20PTI%20leaders%20were%20coerced%20into%20abandoning%20Imran%20Khan.%20Consequently%2C%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20again%20in%20early%20August%20after%20his%20conviction%20in%20one%20of%20the%20many%20cases%20pending%20against%20him%2C%20there%20was%20not%20a%20whimper%20of%20protest%20from%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGranted%20bail%20by%20the%20Islamabad%20High%20Court%2C%20he%20has%20been%20detained%20in%20yet%20another%20case.%20The%20army%20is%20bent%20on%20removing%20him%20from%20the%20political%20equation%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20next%20election.%20Its%20task%20may%20be%20rendered%20easier%20when%20the%20current%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20as%20pro-Imran%2C%20retires%20in%20mid-September%20to%20make%20way%20for%20Qazi%20Faez%20Isa%2C%20who%20is%20ill-disposed%20towards%20Imran%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20the%20government%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%20that%20was%20formed%20in%202020%2C%20inter%20alia%2C%20to%20resist%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20interference%20in%20political%20and%20civilian%20affairs%20has%20ended%20up%20strengthening%20its%20hand%20through%20amendments%20to%20the%20Official%20Secrets%20Act%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmendments%20to%20the%20former%20make%20unauthorised%20disclosure%20of%20identities%20of%20members%20of%20intelligence%20agencies%20a%20punishable%20offence%2C%20give%20a%20role%20to%20officials%20of%20the%20intelligence%20agencies%20in%20investigating%20cases%20of%20its%20violation%20and%20in%20the%20process%20entering%20and%20searching%20a%20place%C2%A0or%20person%20without%20a%20warrant%20and%20seizing%20any%20document%20or%20electronic%20device%20by%20way%C2%A0of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmendments%20to%20the%20latter%20make%20defamation%20of%20the%20army%20a%C2%A0punishable%20offence%2C%20bar%20ex-servicemen%20from%20engaging%20in%20activities%20in%20conflict%C2%A0with%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20interest%20(a%20number%20of%20ex-servicemen%20were%20among%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%C2%A0supporters)%20and%20make%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%20applicable%20notwithstanding%20anything%20inconsistent%20in%20any%20other%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20army%20which%20already%20has%C2%A0a%20veritable%20business%20empire%2C%20has%20been%20authorised%20to%20carry%20out%20activities%20related%C2%A0to%20national%20development%20and%20generate%20proceeds%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20its%20serving%20and%C2%A0retired%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20past%20economic%20actions%20%E2%80%93%20some%20of%20which%20were%20questioned%20by%20courts%20from%20time%20to%20time-%20have%20been%20legalised.%20Weeks%20before%20the%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%20laid%20down%20office%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Army%20Chief%20announced%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20a%20Special%20Investment%20Facilitation%20Council%20(SIFC)%20that%2C%20it%20was%20claimed%2C%20would%20attract%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20investment%20from%20the%20Gulf%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20premature%20to%20describe%20the%20SIFC%20as%20a%20game-changer.%C2%A0Similar%20past%20initiatives%20have%20come%20a%20cropper.%20Asim%20Munir%20has%20been%C2%A0emphasising%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%20economy%20in%20his%20speeches.%20The%20army%20has%C2%A0also%20got%2045%2C000%20acres%20of%20land%20from%20the%20Punjab%20government%20for%20%E2%80%98corporate%C2%A0agriculture%20farming%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20next%20election%2C%20due%20constitutionally%20by%20the%20first%20week%20of%20November.%20The%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20government%20hurriedly%20approved%20the%20results%20of%20the%202022%20census%20at%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20its%20tenure%2C%20thereby%20necessitating%20a%20fresh%20delimitation%20of%20constituencies%2C%20a%20time-consuming%20exercise%2C%20which%20would%20push%20the%20polls%20to%20at%20least%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20army%20has%20got%20installed%20a%20constitutionally%20mandated%20caretaker%20government%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%20under%20the%20Prime%20Ministership%20of%20Anwaar-ul-Haq%20Kakar%2C%20a%20Baloch%20politician%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20it.%20A%20law%20enacted%20by%20the%20outgoing%20government%20confers%20extra%20powers%20on%20the%20caretaker%20set%20up%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20equipping%20it%20to%20stabilise%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20the%20apprehension%20of%20a%20prolonged%20tenure%20for%20the%20army-backed%20caretaker%20government.%20For%20now%2C%20the%20army%20is%20in%20firm%20control.%20Asim%20Munir%20would%20like%20to%20see%20a%20hung%20National%20Assembly%20after%20the%20next%20election%2C%20in%20which%20he%20could%20craft%20a%20majority%20of%20his%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20election%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20heavily%20managed%20affair%2C%20thus%20resulting%20in%20a%20government%20bereft%20of%20political%20legitimacy%20and%20incapable%20of%20dealing%20effectively%20with%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20myriad%20problems%2C%20notably%20the%20wobbly%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-army-imran-khan-scorned%5C%22%3EHell%20Hath%20No%20Fury%20Like%20the%20Pakistan%20Army%20Scorned%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20challenge%20to%20the%20army%20was%20not%20a%20democratic%20revolution.%20He%20was%20himself%20a%20creation%20of%20the%20army.%20More%20importantly%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20so%20far%20produced%20no%20civilian%20leader%20capable%20of%20spearheading%20a%20mass%20uprising%20against%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20relatively%20small%20groups%20of%20PTI%20protestors%20attacked%20several%20army%20installations%20in%20May%2C%20there%20was%20no%20mass%20upsurge.%20The%20redressal%20of%20the%20long-standing%20civil-military%20imbalance%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20as%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20about%2C%20would%20be%20the%20culmination%20of%20a%20process%20and%20not%20an%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20little%20leverage%20over%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20internal%20developments%20and%20has%20dealt%20with%20all%20governments%20there%2C%20including%20military%20dictators%2C%20to%20manage%20the%20difficult%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20all%20that%20we%20can%20do%20is%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20events%20in%20Pakistan%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20growing%20instability%20there%20does%20not%20impact%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20further%20stabilisation%20of%20the%20bilateral%20relationship%20beyond%20the%20restored%20ceasefire%20of%20February%202021%20must%20await%20greater%20clarity%20on%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20internal%20dynamics.%20Though%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20control%20has%20been%20reinforced%20by%20the%20recent%20developments%2C%20Asim%20Munir%20may%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20change%20the%20policy%20of%20tactical%20restraint%20vis%20a%20vis%20India%20adopted%20by%20his%20predecessor%20because%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20complex%20internal%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESharat%20Sabharwal%20is%20a%20former%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%3C%2Fem%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20Pakistan%20Conundrum%3A%20Managing%20a%20Complex%20Relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fworld%2Farmys-control-reinforced-in-pakistan-2671057%5C%22%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20with%20permi