%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20relating%20to%20promoting%20enmity%20between%20groups%2C%20injuring%20or%20defiling%20a%20place%20of%20worship%2C%20uttering%20words%20with%20deliberate%20intent%20to%20hurt%20religious%20feelings%20and%20statements%20conducing%20to%20public%20mischief%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FIR%20seen%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20state%20government%20has%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20for%20trying%20to%20create%20more%20clashes%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20chief%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fani%2Fstatus%2F1698582733273088015%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DJ1VjQNDTFWrXclPML16-LA%5C%22%3EN.%20Biren%20Singh%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20names%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20report%20%E2%80%93%20Seema%20Guha%2C%20Bharat%20Bhushan%20and%20Sanjay%20Kapoor%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%2C%20Seema%20Mustafa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20is%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20filed%20by%20one%20Ngangom%20Sarat%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20worker%E2%80%9D%20who%20lives%20in%20Imphal%20West%2C%20and%20refers%20to%20one%20photo%20caption%20in%20the%20report.%20The%20caption%2C%20the%20complaint%20said%2C%20said%20that%20smoke%20was%20rising%20from%20a%20Kuki%20home%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20was%20in%20fact%20the%20home%20of%20a%20forest%20official.%20Based%20on%20this%2C%20the%20complainant%20decided%20that%20the%20report%20is%20false%20in%20entirety%20and%20%E2%80%9Csponsored%20by%20Kuki%20militants%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Editor%E2%80%99s%20Guild%20had%20recognised%20the%20error%20in%20caption%20and%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20regret%20the%20error%20that%20crept%20in%20at%20the%20photo%20editing%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThere%20was%20an%20error%20in%20a%20photo%20caption%20in%20the%20report%20released%20on%20Sep%202.%20The%20same%20is%20being%20rectified%20and%20updated%20report%20will%20be%20uploaded%20on%20the%20link%20shortly.%20We%20regret%20the%20error%20that%20crept%20in%20at%20the%20photo%20editing%20stage%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20(%40IndEditorsGuild)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndEditorsGuild%2Fstatus%2F1698287099265561025%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%203%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20has%20issued%20a%20statement%20against%20the%20FIR%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20strong%20arm%20tactic%20by%20the%20state%20government%20which%20amounts%20to%20intimidation%20of%20the%20apex%20media%20body%20of%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20violence-marred%20Manipur%20needs%20utmost%20attention%20of%20the%20government%2C%20such%20a%20move%20by%20the%20state%20government%20would%20only%20make%20the%20matters%20worse%20and%20would%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20suppress%20the%3Cbr%3E%5Cntruth.%20It%20is%20a%20case%20of%20shooting%20the%20messenger%20rather%20than%20taking%20measures%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Editor%E2%80%99s%20Guild%20report%20had%20said%20that%20several%20reports%20on%20conflict%20coming%20out%20of%20Manipur%20were%20%E2%80%9Cone-sided%E2%80%9D.%20The%20media%20based%20out%20of%20Imphal%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20had%20%E2%80%9Ctransformed%20into%20Meitei%20media%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20ethnic%20violence%2C%20journalists%20of%20Manipur%20wrote%20one-sided%20reports.%20In%20normal%20circumstances%2C%20they%20would%20be%3Cbr%3E%5Cncross-checked%20and%20monitored%20by%20their%20editors%20or%20Chiefs%20of%20Bureaus%20from%20the%20local%20administration%2C%20police%20and%20securi%3Cbr%3E%5Cnty%20forces.%20However%2C%20this%20was%20not%20possible%20during%20the%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Thee%20Meitei%20media%2C%20for%20that%20is%20what%3Cbr%3E%5CnManipur%20media%20seemed%20to%20have%20become%20during%20the%20conflict%2C%20acted%20collectively%20with%20editors%20consulting%20each%20other%20and%20agreeing%20on%20a%20common%20narrative%20e.g.%2C%20agreeing%20on%20common%20language%20to%20report%20an%20incident%2C%20refer%20ring%20to%20certain%20use%20of%20language%20or%20even%20not%20reporting%20an%20event.%20This%20the%20EGI%20team%20was%20told%20was%20because%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20inflame%20the%20already%20volatile%20situation%20further.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EGI%20team%20also%20criticised%20the%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20saying%20it%20had%20made%20matters%20worse%20and%20%E2%80%9Calso%20affected%20the%20media%20because%20local%20news%20gathered%20without%20any%20communication%20links%20was%20not%20sufficient%20to%20give%20a%20balanced%20view%20of%20the%20situation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20fact-finding%20team%20that%20has%20seen%20legal%20action%20after%20publishing%20a%20report%20on%20Manipur.%20In%20July%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-fir-fact-finding-team%5C%22%3Ea%20case%20was%20registered%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Annie%20Raja%2C%20Nisha%20Siddhu%20and%20Deeksha%20Dwivedi%2C%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Federation%20of%20Indian%20Women%E2%80%99s%20team%20in%20Manipur%20and%20had%20said%20in%20their%20report%20that%20Manipur%20was%20seeing%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20violence%E2%80%9D.%20Before%20that%2C%20a%20leading%20academic%20and%20two%20Kuki%20activists%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhyderabad-university-professor-two-kuki-activists-summoned-by-imphal-court-for-int