he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F03%2Favalanche-hits-sumeru-mountain-behind-kedarnath-temple-water-level-of-saraswati-river-rises-2611342.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20quoted%20the%20District%20Disaster%20Management%20Officer%20at%20Rudraprayag%2C%20Nandan%20Singh%20Rajwar%2C%20as%20having%20said%20that%20the%20avalanche%20took%20place%20at%207.30%20am%20and%20that%20no%20loss%20of%20life%20or%20property%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20Disaster%20Management%20Authority%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20avalanche%20occurred%20in%20a%20part%20of%20the%20glacier%20located%20in%20the%20upper%20region%20of%20Charbari%20Tal%2C%20about%20four%20km%20from%20Kedarnath.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20avalanche%20led%20to%20a%20cloud%20of%20snow%20that%20was%20visible%20for%20five%20to%20seven%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20the%20water%20of%20the%20Saraswati%2C%20too%2C%20has%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20incessant%20rain%20and%20the%20increase%20in%20water%20levels%20all%20the%20rivers%20in%20Uttarakhand%20had%20led%20to%20the%20Char%20Dham%20Yatra%20pausing%20for%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBadrinath%20cave-in%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaving-in-of-land-continues-on-highway-to-hindu-shrine-threatening-road-and-river-in-uttarakhand-s-chamoli-district-101693764808993.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20land%20below%20a%20stretch%20of%20highway%20leading%20to%20Badrinath%2C%20one%20of%20the%20stops%20on%20the%20Char%20Dham%20Yatra%2C%20has%20caved%20in%20and%2C%20despite%20efforts%2C%20has%20kept%20sinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20is%20a%20100-kilometre%20stretch%20between%20Pursari%20and%20Maithana%2C%20which%20the%20National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(NHIDCL)%20have%20tried%20to%20fill%20up%20and%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20land%20below%20this%20stretch%20has%20continued%20to%20cave%20in%20towards%20the%20Alaknanda%20river.%20The%20report%20notes%20that%20erosion%20at%20the%20base%20of%20the%20river%20is%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693808146000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04113850%2FScreenshot-2023-09-04-at-11.38.45-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-fresh-avalanches-continuing-cave-ins-worry-pilgrims-and-residents%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20100-kilometre%20stretch%20between%20Pursari%20and%20Maithana%20has%20continued%20to%20subside.%20An%20avalanche%20on%20the%20Sumeru%20mountain%20was%20seen%20yesterday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-fresh-avalanches-continuing-cave-ins-worry-pilgrims-and-residents%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Panel%20Highlights%20Need%20for%20Reform%2C%20Lack%20of%20Schemes%20for%20Transgender%20Prisoners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2F07210840%2FIMG_3816.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20Committee%20on%20Prison%20Reforms%20has%20recommended%20a%20number%20of%20changes%20to%20the%20current%20functioning%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20prisons%2C%20including%20mandatory%20segregation%20of%20undertrials%2C%20convicts%20and%20first-time%20offenders%20inside%20jails%2C%20while%20producing%20them%20in%20courts%2C%20during%20their%20hospital%20visits%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20issue%20of%20overcrowding%20lies%20majorly%20with%20the%20undertrial%20population%20in%20prisons.%20Many%20states%20have%20a%20high%20number%20of%20undertrial%20prisoners%20who%20are%20languishing%20in%20jails%20for%20years%2C%20awaiting%20trial.%20Speedy%20trial%20can%20become%20the%20effective%20tool%20to%20address%20this%20issue%20and%2C%20hence%2C%20following%20steps%20can%20be%20taken%20in%20this%20regard%3A%20(i)%20special%20fast%20track%20courts%20to%20be%20set%20up%20to%20extensively%20deal%20with%20petty%20offences%20and%20for%20cases%20pending%20for%20five%20years%20or%20more.%20This%20will%20significantly%20put%20a%20curb%20on%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20undertrials%20in%20prisons%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F04%2Fjail-reforms-sc-panel-moots-sweeping-changes-2611471.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20is%20headed%20by%20ex-judge%20Amitava%20Kumar%20and%20comprises%20Director%20General%20of%20Tihar%20Prisons%20and%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Bureau%20of%20Police%20Research%20and%20Development.%20It%20was%20told%20in%202018%20to%20look%20into%20jail%20reforms%2C%20particularly%20around%20aspects%20of%20overcrowding%20in%20prisons%2C%20condition%20of%20women%20and%20children%2C%20transgender%20prisoners%2C%20death-row%20convicts%2C%20semi-open%20or%20open%20jails%2C%20and%20reforms%20in%20juvenile%20correctional%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrison%20authorities%20of%20only%2013%20states%20and%20two%20Union%20Territories%20have%20designated%20a%20%E2%80%98complaint%20officer%E2%80%99%20to%20deal%20with%20complaints%20of%20violation%20of%20rights%20of%20transgender%20inmates%20in%20prisons%20as%20mentioned%20under%20Section%2011%20of%20Transgender%20Persons%20(Protection%20of%20Rights)%20Act%2C%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20committee%20noted.%20%E2%80%9CMajority%20of%20the%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20have%20not%20formulated%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20transgender%20prisoners.%20Existing%20welfare%20schemes%20are%20being%20extended%20to%20them.%20Only%20seven%20states%20and%20two%20Union%20Territories%20%C2%A0have%20specifically%20provided%20the%20measures%20taken%20by%20prison%20authorities%20to%20facilitate%20their%20access%20to%20the%20relevant%20welfare%20schemes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flgbtqia%2Ftransgender-prisoners-india%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20highlighted%20in%20a%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20transgender%20prisoners%20in%20India%20face%20multiple%20problems%20including%20sexual%20violence%2C%20harassment%20and%20misgendering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20order%20that%20this%20report%20should%20be%20made%20public%2C%20and%20asked%20the%20amicus%20curiae%20to%20provide%20copies%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20all%20states.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-seeks-views-of-centre-states-on-prison-reforms-report-in-3-weeks-101693328339576.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Hima%20Kohli%20and%20Rajesh%20Bindal%20said%20that%20it%20will%20first%20consider%20the%20issues%20pertaining%20to%20women%20and%20children%2C%20transgender%20prisoners%20and%20death%20row%20convicts%20and%20later%20address%20the%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20that%20a%20related%20issue%20not%20dealt%20with%20by%20the%20committee%20focused%20on%20replanning%20and%20relocation%20of%20jails.%20%E2%80%9COld%20jails%20in%20cities%20are%20mostly%20single-storeyed.%20These%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20multi-storeyed%20as%20jails%20will%20not%20be%20having%20additional%20space%20to%20expand%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judges%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693806428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewi