C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20called%20the%20animal%20care%20helpline%20and%20the%20police%20to%20rescue%20the%20cow.%20I%20was%20relieved%20but%20also%20realised%20how%20selfless%20animals%20can%20be.%20Buttercup%20was%20tired%20as%20well%2C%20but%20she%20forgot%20her%20problems%20and%20wanted%20to%20help%20another%20life%20in%20distress%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yati%20and%20buttercup%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328587%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYati%20with%20his%20rescue%20dog%20Buttercup.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Yati%20Gaur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChoosing%20the%20road%20less%20travelled%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20cinematography%20from%20Noida%2C%20Yati%20wanted%20to%20do%20a%20masters%2C%20but%20instead%20chose%20to%20work%2C%20earn%20his%20pocket%20money%2C%20and%20get%20some%20practical%20experience%20before%20joining%20a%20course.%20He%20got%20a%20job%20in%202017%20at%20Hostellers%2C%20a%20backpackers%20hostel%20chain%2C%20in%20his%20city%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%2C%20he%20says%2C%20changed%20his%20life%20for%20good.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20biggest%20turning%20point%20in%20my%20life.%20Watching%20other%20travellers%20made%20me%20understand%20how%20travelling%20could%20be%20fun.%20I%20used%20to%20be%20a%20fool%20dreaming%20about%20making%20movies%20about%20other%20countries%20while%20our%20India%20was%20exploding%20with%20culture.%20I%20was%20convinced%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20as%20much%20time%20as%20I%20could%20travelling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20expressed%20to%20my%20father%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20travel%20the%20country.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20if%20travelling%20is%20what%20makes%20me%20happy%2C%20I%20should%20leave%20my%20job%20and%20do%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20enough%20motivation%20for%20me%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20this%20idea.%20My%20father%20also%20offered%20to%20support%20me%20financially%20once%20I%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297672%2Fkashmir-couple-start-animal-rescue-shelters-for-wounded-animals%2F%5C%22%3Eexhaust%20my%20savings.%3C%2Fa%3E%20However%2C%20when%20I%20told%20my%20family%20that%20I%20planned%20to%20travel%20on%20foot%2C%20their%20reaction%20was%20exactly%20what%20I%20expected%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yati%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20planning%20on%20going%20to%20Kedarnath%20and%20my%20mother%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3Esanyasi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(hermit)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20laughing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtbmjr-KNHb%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C