20on%20foot%2C%20in%20September%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20came%20back%20home%2C%20I%20was%20greeted%20with%20the%20warmest%20reception.%20My%20mother%20was%20certainly%20happy%20that%20I%20did%20not%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3Esanyasi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20my%20father%20was%20proud%20of%20my%20achievements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20expedition%20that%20Yati%20went%20on%20covered%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20but%20that%20trip%20was%20cut%20short%20as%20he%20sustained%20an%20injury%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20these%20locations%2C%20Yati%20also%20explored%20northeast%20India%2C%20mainly%20Sikkim%2C%20as%20his%20fourth%20expedition.%20Buttercup%20could%20not%20accompany%20him%20then%20as%20she%20was%20still%20a%20puppy%20and%20needed%20training.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20saw%20that%20Buttercup%20was%20old%20enough%20to%20accompany%20me%20for%20my%20fifth%20expedition%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20train%20her.%20We%20started%20with%20small%20walks%20in%20our%20nearby%20local%20areas%20and%20then%20progressed%20to%20hiking%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20Once%20I%20could%20see%20that%20she%20was%20ready%2C%20we%20started%20travelling%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20Buttercup%20the%20best%20travel%20buddy%20he%20could%20have%20asked%20for%2C%20he%20says%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20smart%20and%20resilient.%20Whenever%20I%20am%20about%20to%20give%20up%2C%20she%20gives%20a%20little%20shake%20as%20if%20to%20say%20%3Cem%3Echalo%20%3C%2Fem%3E(let%E2%80%99s%20go).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1-1693402402.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22yati%20and%20buttercup%20are%20on%20an%20expedition%20of%20walking%20to%20the%20fo